\id MAT - DŇ©ya Translation Project
\h Umatta
\toc1 Isarhe Iyiki Ize iyi Umatta aka ats…õng
\toc2 Umatta
\toc3 Umat
\mt2 Isarhe Iyiki Ize iyi
\mt1 Umatta
\mt2 aka ats…õng
\imt1 Utsutson ri itsi ubvur Umatta
\ip Awu Umatta ats…õng ubvur uwur…õ. Unga awu utsa Uyahuda, unying ra angw…õŐÉ imesu Uyesu.
\ip Ubvur uwur…õ ud…õyiwe ug…õ Uyesu unga awu Ukiristo ha umb…Ē aka abemuwa ru ibibemuwe-Num iyiki igbe, unga awu unerwi abi Uyahuda aka atsu am…õnmb…Ē ug…õ ibanga. Idikinga irh…õirh…õ ubvur uwur…õ uku uyisu Uyesu ug…õ, <<Ungw…õŐÉ Udauda>>. Nu ngge iki iwe ug…õ Isarhe Iyiki Ize ha isi ikpongge iyiy…õi akarh√£rh√£ ra abi Uyahuda, rimi h√£ icicang ishingge Isarhe Iyiki Ize iyi Uyesu Ukiristo iwu iyi anera kishoo ru upfunga, ra abi Uyahuda nu abirab…õ aka asi iwemb…Ē abi Uyahuda.
\ip Ru ubvur Umatta, ats…õng imesu Uyesu ra agb…õr akag…Ēng at…ĒŐÉ…ĒŐÉ. Aki inggbaashia awu imesu Uyesu ni itsi igŇ©, iyiriy…õ iki id…õyiwe ikpŇ© isisei ha abika ad…Ēsa aka isei ri ibib…õkmb…Ē (arherhe aki \xt 5‚ÄĒ7\xt*). Ik…õi imesa iy…Ē…Ē iwengge ri itsi itsery…õ uner itser Uyesu iki im…õŐÉ…õŐÉ unga akorhe (arherhe aki 10). Ik…õi ats…õngmb…Ē nyaka arherhe urh…õrh…õ ri itsi iy…õrha af√£ (arherhe aki 13). Nu imesa ri itsi am…õnk…õ aka am…õŐÉ…õŐÉ uner uku ud…Ēsa awerake nu ikpŇ© if…õrh…õ ha iki im…õŐÉ…õŐÉ unga akorhe (arherhe aki 18). Ra arherhe aki imaataka, Umatta ad…õyiwe nggaa itsery…õ Uyesu aka adzowe abika ad…Ēsa, ngge iwu itser iyiki idzowe Isarhe Iyiki Ize.
\iot Abink…õ aka awe um…Ē
\io1 Atoku Uyesu nu imarnga \ior (1.1‚ÄĒ2.23)\ior*
\io1 UdŇ©w√£ Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima \ior (3.1-12)\ior*
\io1 Isorhu ub…Ētisima Uyesu nu iviviranga \ior (3.13‚ÄĒ4.11)\ior*
\io1 Itser Uyesu ru Ugarhirhi \ior (4.12‚ÄĒ18.35)\ior*
\io1 Izizń© Uyesu ru Urusharhima \ior (19.1‚ÄĒ20.34)\ior*
\io1 Usati Uyesu ukpu imaatak ru Urusharhima \ior (21.1‚ÄĒ27.31)\ior*
\io1 Inyinyapuwe Uyesu nu akpenga \ior (27.32-66)\ior*
\io1 Isisok Uyesu nu idzidzekanga \ior (28.1-20)\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Ubvur atoku Uyesu
\p 
\v 1 Ubvur unang Uyesu Ukiristo, ungw…õŐÉ Udauda uwuruwi aka awu ungw…õŐÉ Uibrahim.
\li1 
\v 2 Uibrahim unga awu ut…õ Uishaku,
\li1 Uishaku unga awu ut…õ Uyakubu,
\li1 Uyakubu unga awu ut…õ Uyahuda nu angw…õŐÉmb…Ē,
\li1 
\v 3 Uyahuda unga awu ut…õ Ufereza nu Uzera, uyisumb…Ē aka awu Utamar,
\m Ufereza unga awu ut…õ Uhezuron,
\li1 Uhezuron unga awu ut…õ Uaram,
\li1 
\v 4 Uaram unga awu ut…õ Uamminadab,
\li1 Uamminadab unga awu ut…õ Unashon
\li1 Unashon unga awu ut…õ Usarhmon,
\li1 
\v 5 Usarhmon unga awu ut…õ Ubo'aza. Urahab unga amar Ubo'aza,
\li1 Ubo'aza unga awu ut…õ Uobida. Urut unga amar Uobida,
\li1 Uobida unga awu ut…õ Ujesse,
\li1 
\v 6 Ujesse unga awu ut…õ Uy…õrhe Udauda.
\p Udauda unga awu ut…õ Usorhomon. Uts…õrha Uriya unga amar Usorhomon,
\li1 
\v 7 Usorhomon unga awu ut…õ Urhehobowam,
\li1 Urhehobowam unga awu ut…õ Uabijah,
\li1 Uabijah unga awu ut…õ Uasa,
\li1 
\v 8 Uasa unga awu ut…õ Uyehoshafat,
\li1 Uyehoshafat unga awu ut…õ Uyoram,
\li1 Uyoram unga awu ut…õ Uazariya,
\li1 
\v 9 Uazariya unga awu ut…õ Uyotam,
\li1 Uyotam unga awu ut…õ Uahaz,
\li1 Uahaz unga awu ut…õ Uhezekiya,
\li1 
\v 10 Uhezekiya unga awu ut…õ Umanasse,
\li1 Umanasse unga awu ut…õ Uaman,
\li1 Uaman unga awu ut…õ Uyosiya,
\li1 
\v 11 Uyosiya unga awu ut…õ Uyekoniya nu angw…õŐÉmb…Ē ri ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka akarha umb…Ē azń© abń© akase ru Ubabirha.
\p 
\v 12 Umb…Ē aka akarha umb…Ē azń© atsń© abń© akase ru Ubabirha,
\li1 Uyekoniya unga awu ut…õ Usheyarhtiyerh,
\li1 Usheyarhtiyerh unga awu ut…õ Uzerubaberh,
\li1 
\v 13 Uzerubaberh unga awu ut…õ Uabihudu,
\li1 Uabihudu unga awu ut…õ Uerhiyakim,
\li1 Uerhiyakim unga awu ut…õ Uazor,
\li1 
\v 14 Uazor unga awu ut…õ Uzadak,
\li1 Uzadak unga awu ut…õ Uakim,
\li1 Uakim unga awu ut…õ Uarhiyud,
\li1 
\v 15 Uarhiyud unga awu ut…õ Uerhiyeza,
\li1 Uerhiyeza unga awu ut…õ Umatana,
\li1 Umatana unga awu ut…õ Uyakubu,
\li1 
\v 16 Uyakubu unga awu ut…õ Uyusuf utsaka Umaryamu, uya Uyesu, umb…Ē aki iyisa Ukiristo.
\p 
\v 17 Kishoo andanna udzur ri Uibrahim uba utsń© Udauda awu us…Ēka na anaa. Udzur nu Udauda uba utsń© ri ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka akarha abi Uisrairha azń© abń© akase ru Ubabirha, andanna awu us…Ēka na anaa. Udzur um…Ē uba utsń© Ukiristo, andanna awu us…Ēka na anaa.
\s1 Imar Uyesu Ukiristo
\r (Irh 2.1-7)
\p 
\v 18 Imar Uyesu Ukiristo iwe rimin…õ. Uyanga Umaryamu awu ukarh Uyusuf. Umb…Ē anasi ipfunumb…Ē, nu umb…Ē any√£ unga awu ra anaa ru ubok Ipfu Isarsatangge.
\v 19 Ukarhnga Uyusuf arhiku uner asi ibeenga idzowe unga atsa ra asu anera, unga akaif…õrhk…Ē iyiki ib…Ēre unga ri iw…Ēk.
\p 
\v 20 B…Ēr unga ana akaif…õrhk…Ē ak…õr…õ ha na arheyirh…Ē any√£ ipfu itser Uteijee kap…õ…õng ru unga ni ig…Ēr unga ig…õ, <<A Uyusuf ungw…õŐÉ Udauda, niba ugŇ©o iwei iy…õi Umaryamu unga awu uts…õŐÉngo, ubinkutsu anaa h√£ unga aka ak…ĒŐÉ adzeki Ipfu Isarsatangge.
\v 21 Awuri imar ungw…õŐÉ nu ungo utare itsoknga igburh Uyesu, ubinkutsu unga awuri if…Ērh anernga ra arhimmb…Ē.>>
\p 
\v 22 Kishoo ak…õr…õ ha akorhe rimi ngge itsuif…õr ubinkpi Uteijee aka arherhe ra angwń© uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num ag…õ,
\v 23 <<Unakugbń©rhń© awuri ik…ĒŐÉ anaa na amar ungw…õŐÉ umb…Ē ayisi itsoknga Uimmanuwerh,>> agbena agburh <<Unum awu nggu um…õn.>>\f + \fr 1.23 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uish 7.14\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 24 Ivangy…õ Uyusuf aka azir ru urh…Ē, unga ad…Ēsa arherhe ha ipfu itser Uteijee iki irherhe na ay…õi Umaryamu unga awea uts…õŐÉnga.
\v 25 B…Ēr asi irhaa nggu unga uts…õku unga aka amar ungw…õŐÉnga. Uyusuf atare itsoknga igburh Uyesu.
\c 2
\s1 Abika ahw…õng √≠dz…õ…õr adzek // udiki iny…õŐÉnum aba iyepa
\p 
\v 1 Ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka amar Uyesu ru uteu Ubaitarhami ru Uyahudiya ri ivang Uhiridu aka awu uy…õrhe, abika ahw…õng √≠dz…õ…õr adzeki ig…ĒŐÉkpee aba Urusharhima.
\v 2 Na arhusa ag…õ, <<Ungw…õŐÉ h√£ umb…Ē aka amar awe rin…õ…õ uy…õrhe abi Uyahuda? Um…õn iny√£m…õn idz…õrnga ri ig…ĒŐÉkpee nu um…õn ń©ba idzowe unga ig…Ēng.>>
\p 
\v 3 Ivangy…õ Uy…õrhe Uhiridu aka agŇ© rimi, am…õnnga adake nu kishoo abi Urusharhima.
\v 4 Ivangy…õ unga aka ak…Ēng kishoo ateiya abika adzowe id…õm-Num nu abika amesuwe Ikpem, unga arhusa umb…Ē anangk…õ umb…Ē aka imar Ukiristo.
\v 5 Umb…Ē ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ru uteu Ubaitarhami ru Uyahudiya. Ubinkpi uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num aka ats…õng,
\q1 
\v 6 << <B…Ēr ungo, Ubaitarhami ra abń© Uyahuda,
\q2 ungo usi iwe…Ē uwuku uci ri iteu Uyahuda.
\q1 Ubinkutsu awu ru ungo
\q2 uy…õrhu uw…Ē…Ē aka idzeka,
\q1 uwuruwi aka idarh anermum Uisrairha.> >>\f + \fr 2.6 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Umik 5.2\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 7 M…Ēc…õ Uhiridu agh…ĒŐÉrh√£ ayisa abika ahw…õng √≠dz…õ…õr ha arhusa abee ihw…õng ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka any√£ idz…õ…õr ha.
\v 8 M…Ēc…õ unga adene umb…Ē azń©mb…Ē Ubaitarhami ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka azń© angw…õŐÉdz…õn na arhisuwa irheng ungw…õŐÉ h√£. Ivangy…õ umbi aka any√£mbi unga, umbi aba as…Ēma umum nu umum igamum izń© indzowe unga ig…Ēng.>>
\p 
\v 9 Umb…Ē aka agŇ© arherhe uy…õrhe amaa, umb…Ē azń©mb…Ē udń©mb…Ē. Idz…õ…õr ha umb…Ē aka any√£ ri ig…ĒŐÉkpee ha iz…õŐÉrh√£ ra asumb…Ē, umb…Ē ad…Ēsa ngge uts…õku ngge iki iba id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ra anangk…õ ungw…õŐÉ h√£ aka awe.
\v 10 Ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka any√£ idz…õ…õr ha, umb…Ē ag…Ēm angg…Ēm akarh√£rh√£.
\v 11 Umb…Ē aka atsń© ri iya ha, umb…Ē any√£ irheng ungw…õŐÉ h√£ nggu uyanga Umaryamu, umb…Ē atararhu ra anangnga adzowe unga ig…Ēng. M…Ēc…õ umb…Ē agarha akpokamb…Ē adzowe √≠zŇ©w√£ uzinarhi nu atsei umb…Ē iki iyisa ufirankisen nu umur.
\v 12 Umb…Ē aka awu ri irheyirh…Ē, Unum ad…õyika umb…Ē niba ibvui azń©mb…Ē ru Uhiridu. Umb…Ē ad…Ēsu udń© ukp…Ē…Ē azń©mb…Ē abń©mb…Ē.
\s1 Atń© azń©mb…Ē Umasar
\p 
\v 13 Umb…Ē aka azń©mb…Ē, Uyusuf arheyirh…Ē any√£ ipfu itser Uteijee iki ig…Ēr unga ig…õ, <<Usisok, ushupu irheng ungw…õŐÉ h√£ nu uyanga na atń© azń©mbi abń© Umasar. √Äka asei ngg…Ē…Ē ha uts…õku umum iki ind…õyiwa umbi. Uhiridu awuri ibeenga irheng ungw…õŐÉ h√£ na af…õre unga.>>
\v 14 Nggee unga asok ashupu irheng ungw…õŐÉ h√£ nu uyanga ru untsuuka akŇ© azń©√£ Umasar.
\v 15 Umb…Ē asei ngg…Ē…Ē ha uts…õku Uhiridu aka akpe. Ak…õr…õ ha akorhe rimi ngge itsuif…õr ubinkpi Uteijee aka arherhe ra angwń© uner uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num ag…õ, <<Umum iyisu ungw…õŐÉmum adzek ru Umasar.>>\f + \fr 2.15 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uho 11.1\xt*\ft .\f*
\s1 Af…õyiwe aw…õkaci ru Uyahudiya
\p 
\v 16 Ivangy…õ Uhiridu aka ahw…õng ug…õ abika ahw…õng √≠dz…õ…õr ha arh…õm unga, unga agŇ© av…Ēm akarh√£rh√£. Unga atsu umb…Ē af…õyiwe irheng aw…õkatsa kishoo ru Ubaitarhami nu ik√£w√£ngge, udzur ra aw…õkatsa abi im…õka ivaa uba ra andzing. Unga akorha ak…õr…õ ha ubinkutsu udzur ri ivang h√£ abika ahw…õng √≠dz…õ…õr ha aka as…Ēme unga imar ungw…õŐÉ h√£ iki iwe im…õka ivaa.
\v 17 Ivang h√£ niy…Ē ngge iki itsuif…õr ubinkpi uner uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uirimiya aka arherhe ag…õ,
\q1 
\v 18 <<AgŇ©mb…Ē urh…õm ru Urama,
\q2 idid…Ēng nu ifakpe irh…õirh…õ,
\q1 Urahirha unga ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ iciu akpe angw…õŐÉnga,
\q2 na akp…õŐÉ…õŐÉ iy…õi id…Ēngam…õn ru unera,
\q1 ubinkutsu aka ashemb…Ē.>>\f + \fr 2.18 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uiri 31.15\xt*\ft .\f*
\s1 Abvui azń© Unazarat
\p 
\v 19 Uhiridu aka akpe, Uyusuf arheyirh…Ē ru Umasar any√£ ipfu itser Uteijee iki ig…Ēr unga ig…õ,
\v 20 <<Usok ushupu irheng ungw…õŐÉ h√£ nu uyanga ukŇ© uzń© abń© Uisrairha. Abika abee if…õr ungw…õŐÉ h√£ aka akpemb…Ē.>>
\p 
\v 21 Nggee unga asok, ashupu ungw…õŐÉ nu uyanga akŇ© azń©√£ abń© Uisrairha.
\v 22 B…Ēr unga aka agŇ© ug…õ Uarkirhayu ungw…õŐÉ Uhiridu aka anyangu ukam ut…õnga awu uy…õrhe Uyahudiya, unga agŇ©√£ iwei izń© ngg…Ē…Ē ha. B…Ēr unga aka arheyirh…Ē umb…Ē agbiite atonga, unga atsń©√£ ru Ugarhirhi.
\v 23 Azń© aseisa ru uteu ukp…Ē…Ē umb…Ē iki iyisa Unazarat. Ngge itsuif…õr ubinkpi abika as…Ēm Arherhu-Num aka arherhe ag…õ, <<Awuri iyisa unga uner Unazarat.>>
\c 3
\s1 Isarhe Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima
\r (Umar 1.1-8; Irh 3.1-18; Uyoh 1.19-28)
\p 
\v 1 Ivang h√£ niy…Ē Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima aka aba adzowe isarhe ra arhum Uyahudiya,
\v 2 anu ig…Ēr ag…õ, <<√Äka adzipa, Iy…õrhe af√£ iki iyongge!>>
\v 3 Uner ha nuw…Ē uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uishaya aka arherhe ra arherhanga ag…õ,
\q1 <<Urh…õm uw…Ē…Ē uyisa ra arhum ug…õ,
\q2 <√Äka agbishuwe udń© Uteijee,
\q1 √†ka avii atsń©ndń©√£ uku urhirhiki ru unga!> >>\f + \fr 3.3 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uish 40.3\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 4 Atorho Uyohana awu igwar urhakumi, abow ikp…Ēm ubvur nu upfurhsń©nga. Ubinghanga uwu asusu nu utoo arhum.
\v 5 M…Ēc…õ aner Urusharhima nu abi Uyahudiya kishoo nu abń© ak…Ē…Ē ru ugb…õr Az…õŐÉ Urdun adzeyi aba ru unga.
\v 6 Ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ as…Ēm arhimmb…Ē nu unga asorhuwe umb…Ē ub…Ētisima ra Az…õŐÉ Urdun.
\p 
\v 7 B…Ēr unga aka any√£ abi Ufarisi nu abi Usaduki arh…õrh…õ aka aba ra anangk…õ unga aka ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ isorhu ub…Ētisima, unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi angw…õŐÉ √≠bvui! Ungaa ad…õyiwa umbi itń© av…Ēm Unum aka iba unuma?
\v 8 √Äka at…ĒŐÉ itsery…õ iki id…õyiwe idzidzipambi.
\v 9 √Äka aneke ikaif…õrhk…Ē ra am…õnmbi ag…õ, <Uibrahim unga awu ut…õm…õn.> Umum id…õyiwa umbi Unum awea ri ijee unga aka itsu atarh ak…õr…õ ake awe aw…õkaci ru Uibrahim.
\v 10 Aka atsumb…Ē angg√£i ru unang acucii. Ub…õn ucucii uku usi ighw…õrmgb…Ē ikpŇ©rh√£ iyiki ize, awuri igb…õr umgb…Ē atsu ru urha.
\p 
\v 11 <<Umum ikorhuwa umbi ub…Ētisima nggu am…õŐÉ utsar idzidzipambi. B…Ēr uwuruwi aka ananga umum ijee nggaw…Ē awuri iba ru undzingmum, abadaknga umum isi √≠m…õŐÉ…õŐÉmum ishipa. Unga awuri isorhuwa umbi ub…Ētisima nggu Ipfu Isarsatangge nu urha.
\v 12 Akp…Ēm nggu utaknga, awuri its…õki ishaa itsemnga na akarha ngge atsuku ungbanga na akpń©ń©we uhweenga ru urhakpi uku usi √≠rhimkp…Ē.>>
\s1 Ub…Ētisima Uyesu
\r (Umar 1.9-11; Irh 3.21-22)
\p 
\v 13 M…Ēc…õ Uyesu aka adzeku Ugarhirhi aba ru Uyohana asorhuwe unga ub…Ētisima ra Az…õŐÉ Urdun.
\v 14 Uyohana abee ik…õn unga, ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<Umum ibee ungo usorhuwa umum ub…Ētisima, ungo usok uba ru umum?>>
\p 
\v 15 B…Ēr Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Uneke ngge iwe rimi ic…õr…õ. Azea um…õn ikorhe ri imin…õ ngge itsuif…õr kishoo ubinkpi Unum aka abee.>> M…Ēc…õ Uyohana abemuwe unga.
\p 
\v 16 Umb…Ē aka asorhuwe Uyesu ub…Ētisima, unga adzeka ra am…õŐÉ. Kanying af√£ ayanga, unga any√£ Ipfu-Num iki icipuwa ru nyaku unurh…õu, iba isei nu unga.
\v 17 M…Ēc…õ urh…õm udzeka af√£ ug…Ēr ug…õ, <<Uw…õr…õ unga awu Ungw…õŐÉmum ukpekŇ© iki ibema. Nggu unga umum igŇ©ib…õn akarh√£rh√£.>> \fig Ipfu-Num iki icipuwa ru nyaku unurh…õu|alt="Spirit of God descend like a dove" src="DN00410b.tif" size="col" loc="3.17" copy="Dn" ref="3.16"\fig*
\c 4
\s1 UndenggŇ© adeyi Uyesu
\r (Umar 1.12-13; Irh 4.1-13)
\p 
\v 1 M…Ēc…õ Ipfu-Num idarh Uyesu izń©ngge ra arhum ru UndenggŇ© adeya unga.
\v 2 Uyesu akpem igha ubin inuma is…Ēka inaa nu utsuu nu atenum. Unga aka amaa, imerh if…õr unga.
\v 3 M…Ēc…õ UndenggŇ© aba ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ungo uba uwu Ungw…õŐÉ Unum, utsu atarh ak…õr…õ awu uborodi.>>
\p 
\v 4 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Its…õng Arherhu-Num ig…Ēr ig…õ, <Asi iwea ubingha ukpekŇ© itsu unera ab…õk, b…Ēr ub…õn urh…õm arherhe uku udzeka ra angwń© Unum.>\f + \fr 4.4 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Iva 8.3\xt*\ft .\f*>>
\p 
\v 5 M…Ēc…õ UndenggŇ© ashupa unga azń© ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ afaf√£ nu usarkasar uteu ni itsi uvi Iya-Num.
\v 6 Ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ungo uba uwu Ungw…õŐÉ Unum, utersha ugba nu abń©. Ubinkutsu its…õng Arherhu-Num ig…Ērngge ug…õ,
\q1 << <Unga awuri itsu √≠pfu itsernga ngge ingw…õŐÉdz…õn
\q2 ni ikaa ungo,
\q1 ngge iwuri ikp…Ēm ungo ra afaf√£ ra abokngge,
\q2 utsur ungo ukw…õr…Ē undaidakngo nu utarh.>\f + \fr 4.6 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Amb 91.11,12\xt*\ft .\f* >> \fig Uyesu ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ni itsi uvi Iya-Num|alt="Jesus standing on top of Temple" src="dn00405b.tif" size="col" copy="Darwin Dunham" ref="4.5-7"\fig*
\p 
\v 7 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Its…õng Arherhu-Num ig…Ērngge ik…õi ug…õ, <Ungo niba ivirungo Uteijee Unumngo!>\f + \fr 4.7 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Iva 6.16\xt*\ft .\f*>>
\p 
\v 8 UndenggŇ© ashupa unga ik…õi aden ni itsi igŇ© iy…Ē…Ē iderdetangge, ad…õyiwe unga iy…õrhe upfung nu ig…Ēngngge.
\v 9 Unga ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Kishoo abina ak…õr…õ umum iwuri idzaamum ungo, ungo uba utararhu nu udzaango umum ig…Ēng.>>
\p 
\v 10 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Us…Ēk…Ē ru umum, Ushaitan! Ubinkutsu its…õng Arherhu-Num ig…Ērngge ug…õ, <Udzowe ig…Ēng ru Uteijee Unumngo, nu uwu ug√£rh√£nga ukpekŇ©.>\f + \fr 4.10 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Iva 6.13\xt*\ft .\f*>>
\p 
\v 11 M…Ēc…õ UndenggŇ© ab…Ēruka unga, nu √≠pfu itser-Num iba it…ĒŐÉwe unga itser.
\s1 Uyesu atirhi itsernga ru Ugarhirhi
\r (Umar 1.14-15; Irh 4.14-15)
\p 
\v 12 Uyesu aka agŇ© ug…õ umb…Ē aka atsuke Uyohana ru ugborzń©, unga abvui azń©√£ Ugarhirhi.
\v 13 Ab…Ēruka Unazarat, azń© asesa ru Ukafanahum, ukpurukpi uku uwe ngg…Ē…Ē ra angwń© ukau ukug…Ēng ra abń© Uzeburhun nu Unaftarhi.
\v 14 Ngge itsuif…õr ubinkpi uner uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uishaya aka arherhe ag…õ,
\q1 
\v 15 <<Abń© Uzeburhun nu abń© Unaftarhi,
\q2 aka awu utsń©ndń© ukau ukug…Ēng,
\q2 ugar Az…õŐÉ Urdun,
\q1 Ugarhirhi aka awu atsen abi Uyahuda,
\q1 
\v 16 um…Ē abika asei ru uzń©
\q2 aka any√£mb…Ē nggaa irhirhang.
\q1 Nu abirab…õ aka asei ra abń© aki uzirhzń© akpe,
\q2 irhirhang iki irhangngge ru umb…Ē.>>
\p 
\v 17 Udzur ri ivang h√£ Uyesu aka atirhi idzowe isarhe, ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<√Äka adzipa, Iy…õrhe af√£ iki iyongge!>>
\s1 Uyesu ayisu inera inaa abika adzui ab…õrh
\r (Umar 1.16-20; Irh 5.1-11)
\p 
\v 18 Uyesu az…õŐÉrh√£ nu ubang Ukau Ugarhirhi nukpi, unga any√£ inera ivaa angw…õŐÉyi, Usiman uwuruwi umb…Ē aki iyisa Ubitru nu Uandarawu ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē. Anu itang igber ru ukau, ubinkutsu umb…Ē awu abika adzui ab…õrh.
\v 19 Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka aba ad…Ēsa umum, nu umum iwuri itsu umbi awu abika adzui anera.>>
\v 20 Ivanga unying umb…Ē aneke igbermb…Ē na ad…Ēsa unga.
\p 
\v 21 Unga aka ab…Ēre anang h√£ na azń© any√£ inera ivaa angw…õŐÉyi ik…õi, Uyaku ungw…õŐÉ Uzabadi nu Uyohana ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē. Awu ru ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ nggu ut…õmb…Ē Uzabadi, ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ igbishi √≠gbermb…Ē. Uyesu ayisa umb…Ē.
\v 22 Kanying umb…Ē anekukumb…Ē ukhukh…Ē…Ē ha ru ut…õmb…Ē na ad…Ēsa unga.\fig Unera ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ itang igber ra am…õŐÉ|alt="Person throwing a fishing net into water" src="lb00209b.tif" size="col" loc="4.22" copy="Louise Bass" ref="4.18-22"\fig*
\s1 Uyesu akerhuwe abi irh√£rh√£
\r (Irh 6.17-19)
\p 
\v 23 Uyesu az…õŐÉrh√£ amaa Ugarhirhi, amesuwe ra ab√£ if…õn-Nummb…Ē, adzowe Isarhe Iyiki Ize iyi Iy…õrhe Unum, na akerhuwe ub…õn irh√£rh√£ nu ikpŇ© ighighong anera.
\v 24 Isarhe ri itsinga it…õŐÉrh√£ imaangge abń© Usuriya, anera akŇ© abika agŇ© ighighong akarh√£rh√£ na ahwa ayetnum nggu ikpŇ© √≠rh√£rh√£, nu abi √≠pfu iyiki ibewe, nu abi irh√£rhń© izurh, nu abika af…Ēr uz…õŐÉrh√£ adamb…Ē, unga akerhuwe umb…Ē.
\v 25 Anera arh…õrh…õ aka adzeku Ugarhirhi, nu iteu us…Ēka umb…Ē iki iyisa Udikaforhi, nu Urusharhima, nu Uyahudiya nu ugar Az…õŐÉ Urdun ad…Ēsa unga.
\c 5
\s1 Idorh ni itsi igŇ©a
\r (Irh 6.20-23)
\p 
\v 1 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka any√£ ikik…Ēng anera arh…õrh…õ, unga afŇ© asei ni itsi igŇ©a. Angw…õŐÉ imesanga aba ru unga.
\v 2 Unga atirha amesuwe umb…Ē ag…õ,
\q1 
\v 3 <<Idorh iwu iyi abirab…õ aka awe atsŇ©w√£ ri ipfumb…Ē,
\q2 ubinkutsu Iy…õrhe af√£ iwu iyimb…Ē
\q1 
\v 4 Idorh iwu iyi abi ighongam…õn,
\q2 ubinkutsu awuri id…Ēngukumb…Ē am…õnmb…Ē.
\q1 
\v 5 Idorh iwu iyi abika ad…Ē…Ēr,
\q2 ubinkutsu ukam upfung
\q2 uwuri iwe ukpumb…Ē.
\q1 
\v 6 Idorh iwu iyi abirab…õ aka agŇ© imerh
\q2 nu ug…ĒŐÉ irhirhika,
\q1 ubinkutsu umb…Ē awuri ishurmb…Ē.
\q1 
\v 7 Idorh iwu iyi abika acucorhe,
\q2 ubinkutsu awuri icorhukumb…Ē umb…Ē.
\q1 
\v 8 Idorh iwu iyi abi am…õn aka at…õn,
\q2 ubinkutsu umb…Ē awuri iny√£mb…Ē Unum.
\q1 
\v 9 Idorh iwu iyi abika atsu idid…Ē…Ēr,
\q2 ubinkutsu awuri iyisa umb…Ē angw…õŐÉ Unum.
\q1 
\v 10 Idorh iwu iyi abika ahwa uver ri irhirhika,
\q2 ubinkutsu Iy…õrhe af√£ iwu iyimb…Ē.
\p 
\v 11 <<Idorh iwu iyimbi ivang anera iki irhena umbi, ay…Ēm umbi, na arherhuwa umbi ikpŇ© iki ibewe ri itsimum.
\v 12 √Äka ag…Ēm akarh√£rh√£, ubinkutsu umbi awuri ikpo itosa irh…õirh…õ ra af√£, ubinkutsu rimi h√£ umb…Ē aka ay…Ēm abika as…Ēm Arherhu-Num abi inggbaashia.
\s1 Angw√£ nu irhirhang
\r (Umar 9.50; Irh 14.34-35)
\p 
\v 13 <<Umbi awu angw√£ abń©√£. B…Ēr angw√£ aba ashike nu itonga ake, awuri ikorha aguse na atsu ake awe angw√£ ik…õi? Awuri ishike ru ugarh, awuri ititare ake na anera az…õŐÉrh√£ nu ake.
\p 
\v 14 <<Umbi awu irhirhang upfung. Uteukpi uku udzin nu igŇ© asi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉ aw…Ēmb…Ē ukp…Ē.
\v 15 Unera asi √≠tsu irhirhang na aw…Ēka ngge ri ikikń©ń©. Nu ngge iki iwe rimi, awuri idene ngge id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ra anang id…õŐÉ…õŐÉngge nu ngge irhange ub…õn unera ri iya.
\v 16 Rimi h√£, √†ka aneke irhirhangmbi irhang ra anera, ngge √≠tsu umb…Ē any√£ itser iyiki izembi na akpoi Ut…õmbi uwu af√£.
\s1 Itsuif…õr iyi Ikpem
\p 
\v 17 <<Niba akaimbi if…õrhk…Ē ug…õ umum ń©ba ifif…ĒŐÉrhuwe √ćkpem Umusa use its…õng abika as…Ēm Arherhu-Num. Umum isi ń©bamum ifif…ĒŐÉrhuwe ngge, b…Ēr umum ń©ba itsu ngge itsuif…õr.
\v 18 Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, uts…õku af√£ nu abń© awuri imaa, uko ishia ra arherhe √ćkpem Umusa isi √≠f…ĒŐÉrhŇ©ngge uts…õku umb…Ē aki itsu abina kishoo atsuaf…õr.
\v 19 Uwuruwi aka azharhuwe ungw…õŐÉrhi ishia unying ri Ikpem na amesuwe anera akorha ngge, awuri iyisa unga uku ucia ri Iy…õrhe af√£, b…Ēr uwuruwi aka ad…Ēsa ngge na amesuwe ngge, awuri iyisa unga nggaa uner ri Iy…õrha af√£.
\v 20 Umum id…õyiwa umbi ug…õ irhirhikambi iba isi inangngge iyi abika amesuwe Ikpem nu abi Ufarisi, umbi asi √≠tsń©mbi ri Iy…õrhe af√£.
\s1 Imesa ri itsi av…Ēm
\r (Irh 12.57-59)
\p 
\v 21 <<Umbi aka agŇ©mbi umb…Ē aka ad…õyiwe atokam…õn isha ag…õ, <√Äka niba af…õrmbi unera,\f + \fr 5.21 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Idzi 5.21\xt*\ft .\f* nu uwuruwi aka af…õr uner awuri itsu uvau nu unga.>
\v 22 B…Ēr umum id…õyiwa umbi uwuruwi aka agŇ© av…Ēm nggu und…Ēkanga awuri itsu uvau nu unga. Ik…õi uwuruwi aka ayisu und…Ēkanga ag…õ, <Ib…õm,> umb…Ē awuri ikŇ©na unga azń© ra anang aka atsu uvau. B…Ēr uwuruwi aka ag…Ēr und…Ēkanga ag…õ, <Ugugge!> unga awuri itsń© ri igbaigba idzŇ©Ň© urha.
\p 
\v 23 <<Nggee, ungo uba ud…õŐÉ…õŐÉngo idzowe izŇ©w√£ nu uyitta ug…õ uw…Ē…Ē awu ra av…Ēm nggu ungo,
\v 24 uneke izŇ©w√£ h√£ ra asu ubeu ha kata. Ugbaashia uzń© umbi agbisha nggu uner ha. M…Ēc…õ nu uba adzowe izŇ©w√£ngo.
\p 
\v 25 <<Unera aba atsuka arherhe ri itsingo ru udzepurhe uku uvarha arherhe, √†ka agbisha nu utsń©ndń© ifetem, iba ishingge rimi unga awuri igbopuwe ungo nggu uwuku atsu uvau, uwuku utsu uvau atsuke ungo ra abok ambow umb…Ē agbange ungo ru ugborzń©.
\v 26 Umum ind…õyiwa ungo idzidz…õrhe, ungo usi √≠dzek…Ē um…Ē uts…õku ungo iki ifai umaa ukobo ha umb…Ē aka atsu ungo ififai.
\s1 Imesa ri itsi arhim itoma-dak
\p 
\v 27 <<Umbi aka agŇ©mbi umb…Ē aka ag…Ēr ag…õ, <Niba utomungo-dak.>\f + \fr 5.27 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Idzi 20.14\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 28 B…Ēr umum id…õyiwa umbi ug…õ ub…õn unera aba arhisa ukuts…õrh irhi any…Ēna, unga aka atomunga-dak nggu uts…õrh ha ra am…õnnga.
\v 29 Usungo ukpu ubok ugha uba uwuri itsuka ungo ra arhim, uhor ukp…Ē utare. Ugba ungo ushi…Ē ru ugau ukp…Ē…Ē ukpu iyorngo nu umb…Ē aka itare iyorngo kishoo ri idzŇ©Ň© urha.
\v 30 Ubok ughango uba itsukakp…Ē arhim ru ungo, uzharha ukp…Ē utare. Ugba ungo ushi…Ē ru ugau ukp…Ē…Ē ri iyorngo nu iyorngo kishoo iki itsń© ri idzŇ©Ň© urha.
\s1 Izharhuwe its…õrh
\r (Umat 19.9; Umar 10.11-12; Irh 16.18)
\p 
\v 31 <<Aka ag…Ērmb…Ē ug…õ, <Uwuruwi aka itsŇ©we uts…õŐÉnga, awu ufang unga adzowe ubvur izharhuwe its…õrh.>\f + \fr 5.31 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Iva 24.1\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 32 B…Ēr umum id…õyiwa umbi ug…õ ub…õn unera aka atsŇ©we uts…õŐÉnga ri ida iwe ru uvau itoma-dak, atsuke unga ru utsń©ndń© itoma-dak. Nu uwuruwi aka apfunu uts…õrh uwuku uwuwayi ha, uner ha atoma-dak.
\s1 Uyirh
\p 
\v 33 <<Ik…õi umbi aka agŇ©mbi umb…Ē aka ad…õyiwe atokam…õn ag…õ, <√Äka niba azharhukumbi uyirh, b…Ēr im…õŐÉ…õŐÉngge ungo utsuf…õr ubinkpi ungo uku uyirhe Uteijee.>
\v 34 B…Ēr umum id…õyiwa umbi ug…õ niba ayirhmbi uyirh. Niba ayirhmbi nggu af√£, ubinkutsu af√£ awu anang isei Unum.
\v 35 Niba ayirhmbi nggu upfung, ubinkutsu awu ubin uku utsorhe andaidaknga, use nggu Urusharhima, ubinkutsu awu uteu Uy…õrhe Ukug…Ēng.
\v 36 Niba uyirh…Ē nggu itsingo, ubinkutsu ungo usi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉ utsu igwar unying iwengge iki iterha use iki ifń©rh√£.
\v 37 Im…õŐÉ…õŐÉngge umbi ag…Ēr ag…õ <ń®ń©> use <ń®'ń©>. Ub…õn ubinkpi uku ut…Ēngkp…Ē rimi idzeku uwuku ubewe ha.
\s1 Ififai
\r (Irh 6.29-30)
\p 
\v 38 <<Umbi aka agŇ©mbi umb…Ē aka ag…Ēr ag…õ, <Unera aba atsŇ©wŇ©ka usungo, umb…Ē atsŇ©we usu ukpunga, nu unera aba atsŇ©wŇ©ka unyń©ń©ngo, umb…Ē atsŇ©we unyń©ń© ukpunga.>\f + \fr 5.38 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Idzi 21.24; Urha 24.20; Iva 19.21\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 39 B…Ēr umum id…õyiwa umbi ug…õ niba afaimbi iyiki ibewe nggu iyiki ibewe. Unera aba akw…õra ungo nu utam ubok ugha, udzipuwe utam ukpu uvaa ik…õi.
\v 40 Unera aba atsuka arherhango ra anang aka atsu uvau na abeenga ivur atorhango, udzowe nggu atorho akag…Ēnga ik…õi.
\v 41 Unera aba atsu ungo uz…õŐÉrhŇ©ngo ru ukirhomita unying, uzń© nggu unga akirhomita avaa.
\v 42 Udzowe uwuruwi aka aba ibibee ru ungo, niba udzipuk…Ē undzing nu uwuruwi aka abee ik…Ēw ru ungo.
\s1 √Äka abema anggamtsakmbi
\r (Irh 6.27-28,32-36)
\p 
\v 43 <<Umbi aka agŇ©mbi umb…Ē aka ag…Ēr ag…õ, <Ubemu und…Ēkango nu ukp…õŐÉ…Ē uwuku ukp…õŐÉ ungo.>\f + \fr 5.43 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Idzi 19.18\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 44 B…Ēr umum id…õyiwa umbi ug…õ, √†ka abemu uwuku ukp…õŐÉ umbi na af…õne-Num ru abika adzaa umbi uver.
\v 45 Rimi h√£ umbi awuri iwe ru nyaka angw…õŐÉ idzidz…õrhe abi Ut…õmbi ra af√£. Unga atsu unum urhang ra abika aze nu abika abewe, na atsu inai idoi ra abika arhurhika nu abirab…õ aka asi irhikumb…Ē.
\v 46 Umbi aba abema abirab…õ aka abema umbi ukpekŇ©, umbi awuri ikpo ikpŇ© ugb…õtu ukusong? Use abika ay…õi ikirbi abń© asi ikorhumb…Ē rimi?
\v 47 Umbi aba akpurha aghwe anermbi, umbi akorhu use anang ab…Ē…Ē? Abi uzń© asi ikorhumb…Ē rimi h√£?
\v 48 √Äka awe andzumunga ri irhirhika, ru nyaku Ut…õmbi uwu af√£ aka awu undzumunga ri irhirhika.
\c 6
\s1 Adzowe izŇ©w√£
\p 
\v 1 <<√Äka angw…õŐÉdz…õn utsur itser iyi irhirhikambi iwengge iyi anera aka iny√£. Umbi aba akorhe rimi, umbi asi √≠kpombi itosa ru Ut…õmbi uwu af√£.
\p 
\v 2 <<Ngge itsu ivangy…õ ungo uku uwuri idzowe abika abubee, niba urherhungo ake ra awiya, ru nyaka abi ukpukpeta aki ikorhe ra ab√£ if…õn-Num nu atsń©ndń© ngge its√ļ anera akpoi umb…Ē. Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, umb…Ē aka ay…õi itosamb…Ē niy…Ē.
\v 3 B…Ēr ivangy…õ ungo uku iyike uner uwuku ububee, niba uneke uner uw…Ē…Ē ahw…õnga ubinkpi ungo uku ikorhe.
\v 4 Ngge √≠tsu izŇ©w√£ ungo ima iwe ri iw…Ēk. M…Ēc…õ Ut…õngo, uwuku uny√£ ri iw…Ēk, ama adzaa itosango.
\s1 If…õn-Num
\r (Irh 11.2-4)
\p 
\v 5 <<Ivang if…õn-Nummbi, √†ka niba awembi ru nyaka abi ukpukpeta, umb…Ē abemi id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ na af…õn-Num ra ab√£ if…õn-Num nu atsń©ndń© ru anera any√£ umb…Ē. Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, umb…Ē aka ay…õimb…Ē undzumu itosamb…Ē.
\v 6 B…Ēr ivangy…õ ungo iki if…õn-Num, utsń© ru ub√£ngo nu uf…Ēme angwń© ub√£√£, uf…õnu Ut…õngo uwuku uwe ri iw…Ēk. Ut…õngo uwuku uny√£ ri iw…Ēk awuri idzidzaanga itosango.
\v 7 Ivangy…õ umbi aka if…õn-Num, √†ka niba adarhumbi ider arherhe ru nyaka abirab…õ aka asi ihw…õngmb…Ē Unum. Umb…Ē akaif…õrhk…Ē ug…õ arherhe urh…õrh…õ uwuri itsu umb…Ē agŇ©.
\v 8 Niba awembi ru nyaka umb…Ē. Ut…õmbi ahw…õnga ubinkpi umbi aka abee nu umbi ad…Ērha af…õna unga.
\p 
\v 9 <<√Äka af…õn-Num rimin…õ,
\q1 << <A Ut…õm…õn ra af√£,
\q1 atsam itsokngo isarsatake.
\q1 
\v 10 Iy…õrhango iba,
\q1 ubinkpi ungo uku ubee umb…Ē akorhe
\q2 ru upfung ru nyaka umb…Ē iki ikorhe ra af√£.
\q1 
\v 11 Uma udzaa ubingham…õn ukpu irher…õ.
\q1 
\v 12 Uma utsŇ©we arhimm…õn,
\q2 ru nyaka um…õn iki isaki itsŇ©we abika ash…Ēng um…õn.
\q1 
\v 13 Niba udarh um…õn uzń©…Ē ru undeya,
\q1 b…Ēr uf…Ērh um…õn ri iyiki ibewe.>
\m 
\v 14 Umbi aba atsŇ©wŇ©kumbi anera aka ash…Ēng umbi, Ut…õmbi uwu af√£ awuri itsŇ©w√£nga umbi.
\v 15 B…Ēr umbi aba asi itsŇ©wŇ©kumbi anera aka ash…Ēng umbi, rimi h√£ Ut…õmbi asi √≠tsŇ©wŇ©ka arhimmbi.
\s1 Ikpem ighabin
\p 
\v 16 <<Ivangy…õ umbi aka ikpem ighabin, niba asherhumbi uny…õŐÉ…õŐÉmbi ru nyaka abi ukpukpeta aki ikorhe, umb…Ē aka isaka asherhu uny…õŐÉ…õŐÉmb…Ē ra anera any√£ umb…Ē aka akpem ighabin. Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, umb…Ē aka ay…õimb…Ē undzumu itosamb…Ē.
\v 17 B…Ēr ivangy…õ ungo uku ukpem…ĒŐÉ ighabin, usorh asungo nu ukpai itsingo nu udzuka atsei,
\v 18 utsur anera ahw…õngmb…Ē ungo uku ukpem ighabin, b…Ēr Ut…õngo ukpekŇ©, aka awu ri iw…Ēk. Nu unga, Ut…õngo aka any√£ ri iw…Ēk, awuri idzidzaanga itosango.
\s1 Iwe ru ubin ra af√£
\r (Irh 12.33-34)
\p 
\v 19 <<Niba ak…Ēng abin angw…õŐÉmbi ru upfung, anangk…õ adzurh nu iviv…ĒŐÉ…ĒŐÉ iki idakuwe ake, nu av…õu aki itsń© av…õu iv…õu.
\v 20 B…Ēr √†ka atsu am…õnmbi ri ikpo ugb…õta ra af√£, anangk…õ adzurh nggu iviv…ĒŐÉ…ĒŐÉ asi √≠dakuke ake, anangk…õ av…õu asi √≠tsń© av…õumb…Ē.
\v 21 Ubinkutsu, anangk…õ abinmbi aka awe, um…Ē am…õnmbi aka iwe ik…õi.
\s1 Irhirhang iyor
\r (Irh 11.34-36)
\p 
\v 22 <<Asu ake awu irhirhang iyor. Asungo aba akerke, iyorngo kishoo iwuri it…Ēk nggu irhirhang.
\v 23 B…Ēr asungo aba asi ikerke, iyorngo kishoo iwuri iwe ru uzń©. Uba irhirhang ru ungo iwu uzń©, nggaa uzń© h√£ uwu uguse!
\p 
\v 24 <<Unera asi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉ at…ĒŐÉwŇ©ka itser ra ateiya avaa. Unga awuri ibema unying na akp…õŐÉ…õŐÉ uw…Ēr…Ē, unga awuri idzowe itsinga ru unying na akp…õŐÉ…õŐÉ uw…Ēr…Ē. Ungo usi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉ udzowuk…Ē itsingo ru Unum nu uhw…õk.
\s1 Niba agŇ©mbi ighong
\r (Irh 12.23-31)
\p 
\v 25 <<Nggee umum id…õyiwa umbi, niba agŇ©mbi ighong ru ibib…õkmbi nu ubinkpi umbi aka igha, use ubinkpi umbi aka ihwa, use atorhak…õ umbi aka itsim nu ayormbi. Urh…õ usi inangmgb…Ē ubingha? Iyor isi inangge atorho?
\v 26 √Äka any√£ anunu af√£. Asi idoike asi igb…õrke asi ik…Ēng atsuke ra angban. B…Ēr Ut…õmbi uwu af√£ unga adzowe ighigha ake. Umbi asi iwu ru ugarh anangmbi ake?
\v 27 Ungam…Ē ru umbi igŇ© ighongnga id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ itomungge ivanga unying ri inumy…õ unga aka ib…õk?
\p 
\v 28 <<Awu use utsu umbi agŇ© ighong atorho? √Äka arhi √≠fur arhum iki iseng. Isi it…ĒŐÉngge itser use inuw abin.
\v 29 B…Ēr umum id…õyiwa umbi, uy…õrhe Usorhomon ri ig…Ēngnga kishoo unga anasi igb…õra idzam ru nyaki ifur unying.
\v 30 Unum aba agb…õruka idzam nu ubń©ń© arhum rimi, uku uwe irher…õ nu ud√£ umb…Ē akpń©ń©we ru urha, asi √≠gb…õranga umbi idzam, umbi abi imangmang iyiki ici?
\v 31 Nggee niba agŇ©mbi ighong ag…õ, <Um…õn igha usee?> use <Um…õn ihwa usee?> use <Um…õn itsim usee?>
\v 32 Abi uzń© abee ikpŇ© abin ak…õr…õ ha. Rimi h√£ Ut…õmbi uwu af√£ ahw…õnga umbi abeembi abin h√£.
\v 33 B…Ēr √†ka agbaashia abee Iy…õrhe Unum nu irhirhikanga, nu abin h√£ kishoo awuri idzaamb…Ē umbi ik…õi.
\v 34 Nggee niba agŇ©mbi ighong iyi ud√£, ubinkutsu ud√£ uwu nggu ayetnumkp…Ē. Ub…õn unuma ayetnum am…õŐÉ…õŐÉke nggu ukp…Ē.
\c 7
\s1 Uneke itsu uvau ra anera
\r (Irh 6.37-38,41-42)
\p 
\v 1 <<√Äka aneke itsu uvau ra anera, utsur umb…Ē atsukamb…Ē umbi uvau.
\v 2 IkpŇ© uvauwi umbi aki itsuke anera, ikpŇ© iyi ha umb…Ē aka itsuka umbi. Ugbiuwi umbi aka akŇ© amei, awuri ikŇ© umgb…Ē ha amei adzaa umbi.
\p 
\v 3 <<Awu use utsu ungo urhi umbumbin ru usu und…Ēkango nu usi iny√£…ĒŐÉ ungbŇ©ngkŇ© uku uwe ru usungo?
\v 4 Ungo ukorhu uguse nu ug…Ēr und…Ēkango ug…õ, <Uneke umum itsŇ©w√£ umbumbin ru usungo,> nggay…õ ungbŇ©ngkŇ©wi uwu ru usu ukpungo?
\v 5 Ungo uner ukpukpeta, utirhu utsŇ©we ungbŇ©ngkŇ© ru usungo, m…Ēc…õ nu urhi utai nu utsŇ©we umbumbin ru usu und…Ēkango.
\p 
\v 6 <<√Äka niba adzowukumbi √≠jui abin aka asar. Niba atarkumbi abinarh…Ē aki imang ra arhede. Ake awuri ijang adak na adzipa anayiwa umbi.
\s1 Arhusa, abee, akw…õr angwń© ub√£
\r (Irh 11.9-13)
\p 
\v 7 <<√Äka af…õna awuri idzaamb…Ē umbi. √Äka abee umbi awuri ikpikpombi. √Äka akw…õr angwń© ub√£ awuri itsuruwamb…Ē umbi.
\v 8 Ub…õn unerwi aka af…õna awuri iy…õisa, unga uwuku ububee awuri ikpoa, nu unga uwuku ukw…õr angwń© ub√£ awuri itsurukumb…Ē unga.
\p 
\v 9 <<Awu ungam…Ē ru umbi, ungw…õŐÉnga aba arhusa uborodi, unga awuri idzowe unga utarh?
\v 10 Use unga aba arhusu ub…õrh, unga awuri idzowe unga ibvui?
\v 11 Umbi abi am…õn aka abewe aba ahw…õngmbi idzowe angw…õŐÉmbi abin aka aze, iwuri iwe iguse Ut…õmbi ra af√£ aka idzowe abin aka aze ra abirab…õ aka if…õna unga!
\v 12 Nggee ub…õn ubinkpi umbi aka abee anera akorhuwa umbi, √†ka akorhuwe umb…Ē rimi h√£. Ak…õr…õ kishoo ake awu √ćkpem Umusa nu abika as…Ēm Arherhu-Num.
\s1 Angwń© akika apare nu akika at…õi
\r (Irh 11.9-13)
\p 
\v 13 <<√Äka atsń© ra angwń© ub√£ aka apare. Ubinkutsu anera arh…õrh…õ abika atsń© ra angwń© aka at…õi nu utsń©ndń© uwuku uzń© itsitsń©m, ut…õi.
\v 14 B…Ēr angwń© ub√£ akika apare nu utsń©ndń© uwuku uzń© ibib…õk ughong uz√£rh√£. Abika ad…Ēsa umgb…Ē asi irh…õmb…Ē.
\s1 Ucucii nu ikpŇ©rh√£ngge
\r (Irh 6.43-44)
\p 
\v 15 <<√Äka angw…õŐÉdz…õn nggu abika as…Ēm Arherhu-Num igb…õrangwń©. Umbi awuri iny√£ umb…Ē ru nyaki √≠d…Ēi, b…Ēr idzidz…õrhe umb…Ē awu √≠jui ngbako iy…õ imerh iki if…õr akarh√£rh√£.
\v 16 Umbi awuri ihw…õng umb…Ē ri ikpŇ© itsermb…Ē. Awuri id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ak…Ē…Ērmb…Ē ikpŇ©rh√£ inebi ru ucucii idid…Ēk, use awuri ikpomb…Ē uvorhvo ri idid…Ēk?
\v 17 Rimi h√£ ub…õn ucucii uwuku uze uku usaku ughw…õr ikpŇ©rh√£ iyiki ize, b…Ēr ucucii uku ubewe uku usaku ughw…õr ikpŇ©rh√£ iyiki ibewe.
\v 18 Ucucii uwuku uze usi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ughw…õrmgb…Ē ikpŇ©rh√£ iyiki ibewe, rimi h√£ ucucii uwuku ubewe usi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ughw…õrmgb…Ē ikpŇ©rh√£ iyiki ize.
\v 19 Ub…õn ucucii uku usi √≠ghw…õrmgb…Ē ikpŇ©rh√£ iyiki ize, umb…Ē awuri igb…õr atsuku urha.
\v 20 Nggee, awu ikpŇ©rh√£ke awuri itsu umbi ahw…õng ake.
\s1 Umum isi ihw…õng umbi
\r (Irh 13.25-27)
\p 
\v 21 <<Asi iwea ub…õn unera aka ig…Ēr umum ag…õ, <A Uteijee, a Uteijee,> awuri itsń© ri Iy…õrhe af√£, b…Ēr awu uwuruwi ukpekŇ© aka akorhu ubinkpi Ut…õmum uwuku uwu ra af√£ aka abee.
\v 22 Ru unum h√£ anera arh…õrh…õ awuri ig…Ēr umum ag…õ, <A Uteijee, a Uteijee! Um…õn isi is…Ēmm…õn Arherhu-Num ri itsokngo, nu ri itsokngo um…õn iki iwayiwe √≠pfu iyiki ibewe ri ikorha abin idzeu arh…õrh…õ?>
\v 23 M…Ēc…õ umum iki ig…Ēr umb…Ē ug…õ, <Umum isi ihw…õng umbi. √Äka asombi ru umum, umbi abika akorhe iki ibewe.>
\s1 Uner idzin itsoi nu uguge uner idzin
\r (Irh 6.47-49)
\p 
\v 24 <<Nggee uwuku ugŇ© arherhamum na at…ĒŐÉ itser nggu ake, unga awu ru nyaku uner itsoi uwuruwi aka adzin iyanga ni ifa.
\v 25 M…Ēc…õ inai idoi, am…õŐÉ adzek, ugba uso ukw…õr iya ha. Ike isi igbake ubinkutsu, adzin ike ni ifa.
\v 26 B…Ēr uwuku ugŇ© arherhamum na akp…õŐÉ…õŐÉ it…ĒŐÉ itser nggu ake, unga awu ru nyaku ugugge uwuruwi aka adzin iyanga nu uzuzeu.
\v 27 Inai idoi, am…õŐÉ adzek, ugba uso ukw…õr iya ha, igbigba ike ibewungge.>>
\p 
\v 28 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka amaa irherhe abin ak…õr…õ, ikik…Ēnga idzedzeu imesanga,
\v 29 ubinkutsu unga amesuwe umb…Ē ru nyaku unerwi aka awe ru ijee, asi iwea ru nyaka abika amesuwe Ikpemmb…Ē.
\c 8
\s1 Uner ingbim
\r (Umar 1.40-45; Irh 5.12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka acipuwa ri igŇ© h√£, anera arh…õrh…õ aka ad…Ēsa unga.
\v 2 Uner ingbim uw…Ē…Ē aba atararhu ra anangnga na ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<A uteiya, ungo uba ubemungo, ungo ud…õŐÉ…õŐÉ usarango umum.>>
\p 
\v 3 Uyesu aberu uboknga abanga unga na ag…õ, <<Umum ń©beemum, usar!>> Kanying ingbimnga ikerhungge.
\v 4 M…Ēc…õ Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Niba ud…õyik…Ē unera. B…Ēr uzń©, ud…õyiwe itsingo ru uwuku udzowe id…õm-Num, nu udzowe izŇ©w√£ ru nyaki √ćkpem Umusa iki itsu. Ngge iwe ideka ru umb…Ē ug…õ ungo uku ukerhungo.>>
\s1 Imangmang unggbaashi // abi iwa Uroma
\r (Irh 7.1-10; Uyoh 4.43-54)
\p 
\v 5 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka atsń© ru Ukafanahum, uteiya abi iwa Uroma uw…Ē…Ē aba ash…ĒŐÉrhŇ© Uyesu ama ayike unga.
\v 6 Ag…õ, <<A uteiya, ug√£rh√£mum ashai iyor awe ri iya, anu igŇ© ighong akarh√£rh√£.>>
\p 
\v 7 Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Umum iwuri iba ikerhukŇ© unga.>>
\p 
\v 8 Unggbaashi abi iwa Uroma ha ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<A uteiya, umum isi im…õŐÉ…õŐÉmum ungo iki iba ri iyamum. B…Ēr urherhu urh…õm ukpekŇ©, ug√£rh√£mum h√£ awuri ikerhunga.
\v 9 Umum iwe ru ubok ijee, abi iwa ab…Ē…Ē awu ru ubokmum. Ig…Ēr uw…õr…õ ingg…õ, <Uzń©,> unga azń©√£, nu uw…Ēr…Ē ingg…õ, <Uba,> unga abanga. Umum iba ig…Ēr ug√£rh√£mum ingg…õ, <Ukorhe rimin…õ,> unga akorhe.>>
\p 
\v 10 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka agŇ© rimi, unga adzeidzeu na ag…Ēr abika ad…Ēsa unga ag…õ, <<Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, ru Uisrairha kishoo umum inasi ikpomum uwuku uwe ru imangmang ikerketangge ru nyaki iy…õr…õ ha.
\v 11 Umum ig…Ēr umbi ug…õ anera arh…õrh…õ awuri idzeki ig…ĒŐÉkpee nu udiku urh…õ…õ, aba asei nggu Uibrahim, Uishaku nu Uyakubu agha irhowa ri Iy…õrhe af√£.
\v 12 B…Ēr awuri itare irh…õ abi Uisrairha ra awiya ru uzń©, anangk…õ umb…Ē aka iciu akpe nggu it√£i anyń©.>>
\p 
\v 13 M…Ēc…õ Uyesu ag…Ēr uteiya abi iwa Uroma h√£ ag…õ, <<Uzń©! Iwuri ikorhungge ru nyaka ungo uku uwe ru imangmango.>> Kanying ug√£rh√£nga akerhunga ri ivang h√£.
\s1 Uyesu akerhuwe anera arh…õrh…õ
\r (Umar 1.29-31; Irh 4.38-39)
\p 
\v 14 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka atsń© ri iya Ubitru, unga any√£ uya uts…õrha Ubitru anu nu ukoma iyora imani.
\v 15 Unga abangu uboknga imani iyor ha inekungge unga. Uya ha asok akorhuwe unga ubingha.
\p 
\v 16 Urh…õ…õ uku uwe, umb…Ē akŇ© anera arh…õrh…õ abika awe ru √≠pfu iyiki ibewe aba ru unga. Unga akŇ© irh…õm awayiwe ngge na akerhuwe abi irh√£rh√£ kishoo.
\v 17 Akorha ak…õr…õ ngge itsuif…õr ubinkpi umb…Ē aka arherhe ra angwń© uner uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uishaya ag…õ,
\q1 <<Unga nyanguwe irh√£rh√£m…õn,
\q2 unga akerhuwe ighongam…õn.>>\f + \fr 8.17 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uish 53.4\xt*\ft .\f*
\s1 Ayetnum akika ad…Ēsu Uyesu
\r (Irh 9.57-62)
\p 
\v 18 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka any√£ nggaa ikik…Ēng anera iki idzipa unga, unga atsu umb…Ē agar ukau ha azń© ugar ukp…Ēr…Ē.
\v 19 M…Ēc…õ uner uwuku umesuwe Ikpem aba ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<A umarhem, umum id…Ēsa ungo izń© ub…õn anang ungo iki izń©.>>
\p 
\v 20 Uyesu adzipa ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<√ćjui ngbako iyiki ici iwengge ri ingwń©ngge, anunu ik…õi aweke ra ashiyake, b…Ēr Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner ashia ra anangk…õ unga aka itsu itsinga.>>
\p 
\v 21 Ungw…õŐÉ imesa uw…Ē…Ē ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<A uteiya, uneka umum inggbaashia izń© ń©dzake ut…õmum.>>
\p 
\v 22 B…Ēr Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ud…Ēsa umum, uneke abika akpe adzake abika akpemb…Ē.>> \fig Ijui ngbako iyiki ici nggu angw…õŐÉngge|alt="Fox with babies in foxhole/den" src="bk00051b.tif" size="col" loc="8.22" copy="Louise Bass and Horace Knowles" ref="8.20"\fig*
\s1 Uyesu ad…Ē…Ēte ugba inai
\r (Umar 4.35-41; Irh 8.22-25)
\p 
\v 23 M…Ēc…õ unga atsń© ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ, angw…õŐÉ imesanga ad…Ēsa unga.
\v 24 Kanying ugba ukerketakp…Ē usoyi ru ukau am…õŐÉ h√£, am…õŐÉ asoyi atsń©rh√£ ru ukhukh…Ē…Ē ha. B…Ēr Uyesu awu ru urh…Ē.
\v 25 Angw…õŐÉ imesa azń© azita unga, ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<A uteiya, uf…Ērha um…õn! Um…õn iki iwuri itsń©mm…õn!>>
\p 
\v 26 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi abi imangmang iyiki ici, awu use utsu umbi agŇ© iwei rimi?>> M…Ēc…õ unga asok ats…õrhu ugba nu ubvun ukau ha. Ukp…Ē kishoo ud…Ē…Ēr uku utata.
\p 
\v 27 Anera adzeidzeu na arhusa ag…õ, <<Awu ikpŇ© uner uwukusong nuwi? Ugba nu ubvun ukau ik…õi agŇ©na unga!>>
\s1 Ikikerhuwe inera ivaa // abi ipfu iyiki ibewe
\p 
\v 28 Ivangy…õ unga aka atsń© ugar ukp…Ēr…Ē ra abń© abi Ugadara, inera ivaa abi ipfu iyiki ibewe aka adzek ra anang adzak anera agbopa unga. Umb…Ē awu ubin iwei akarh√£rh√£, ngge itsu anera asi id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ad…Ēsumb…Ē utsń©ndń© h√£.
\v 29 Umb…Ē atsu ivum ag…õ, <<A Ungw…õŐÉ Unum, ungo uba itser use ru um…õn? Ungo uba idzaa um…õn uver ri ivanga id…Ērhi iwe?>>
\p 
\v 30 Ukhapa ru umb…Ē, ukpui arhede arh…õrh…õ ud…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ugh√£w√£.
\v 31 √ćpfu iyiki ibewa ha ish…ĒŐÉrhŇ© Uyesu ig…õ, <<Ungo uba uwayik…Ē um…õn, utsu um…õn itsń© ru ukpui arhede ukp…Ēr…Ē.>>
\p 
\v 32 M…Ēc…õ unga ag…Ēr ngge ag…õ, <<√Äka azń©!>> Ngge idze izń© ru ukpui arhede ha, ake asok atń© acipa nu ughoghor abang ukau ha agba atsń© ra am…õŐÉ akpeke.
\v 33 Abi ugh√£w√£ arhede ha atń© atsń© ru utepa adzowe isarhe ha kishoo, nu ubinkpi uku ukorhe ra abi ipfu iyiki ibewa ha.
\v 34 M…Ēc…õ kishoo anera ru utepa adzek agbangu Uyesu. Ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka any√£ unga, umb…Ē ash…ĒŐÉrh√£ unga ama asoka ra abń©mb…Ē.
\c 9
\s1 Uyesu akerhuwe uner ushayi iyor
\r (Umar 2.1-12; Irh 5.17-26)
\p 
\v 1 Uyesu atsń© ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ, agar azń© uteunga.
\v 2 Aner ab…Ē…Ē akŇ© uner ishayi iyor aba ru unga, anu nu ufar. Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka any√£ imangmangmb…Ē, unga ag…Ēr ushayi iyor ha ag…õ, <<Niba ugŇ©o ighong ungw…õŐÉ ha, umb…Ē aka atsŇ©w√£mb…Ē arhimngo.>>
\p 
\v 3 M…Ēc…õ ab…Ē…Ē abika amesuwe Ikpem ag…Ēr ad…Ēkamb…Ē ag…õ, <<Utsak uwur…õ arhenu Unum!>>
\p 
\v 4 B…Ēr Uyesu ahw…õnga ubinkpi umb…Ē aka akaif…õrhk…Ē, unga ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu umbi akaif…õrhk…Ē iyiki ibewe ra am…õnmbi rimi?
\v 5 Akasong asi ighongke irherhe, ig…Ēr ug…õ, <Umb…Ē aka atsŇ©w√£mb…Ē arhimngo,> use ig…Ēr ug…õ, <Usisok uz…õŐÉrh√£?>
\v 6 B…Ēr umum ibee umbi ahw…õng ug…õ Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner awea ri ijee iyiki itsŇ©we arhim ru upfung.>> M…Ēc…õ unga ag…Ēr ushayi iyor ha ag…õ, <<Usisok ufetu ufarngo uzń© ri iya.>>
\v 7 Nu utsa ha asok azń©√£ ri iyanga.
\v 8 Ivangy…õ ikik…Ēng anera iki iny√£ rimi iwei if…õr umb…Ē. Umb…Ē akpoi Unum, aka adzowe anera ikpŇ© ijee ha.
\s1 Uyesu ayisu Umatiyu
\r (Umar 2.13-17; Irh 5.27-32)
\p 
\v 9 Uyesu awu ru az…õŐÉrh√£ na any√£ utsaw…Ē…Ē agburh Umatiyu asei ra anang aka ay…õi ikirbi abń©. Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Ud…Ēsa umum.>> M…Ēc…õ Umatiyu asok ad…Ēsa unga.
\p 
\v 10 Uyesu asei ighabin ri iya Umatiyu, abika ay…õi ikirbi abń© nu abirab…õ umb…Ē aka anyanga umb…Ē awu abi arhim arh…õrh…õ, aba agha nggu unga nu angw…õŐÉ imesanga.
\v 11 Ivangy…õ abi Ufarisi aka any√£ rimi, umb…Ē arhusa angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu umarhemmbi asei igha ubingha nggu abika ay…õi ikirbi abń© nu abi arhim?>>
\p 
\v 12 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka agŇ© rimi, unga ag…õ, <<Abika aker asi ibeemb…Ē uner ag…Ēu, b…Ēr abi irh√£rh√£ abee.
\v 13 √Äka azń© amesa agben its…õng Arherhu-Num akirak…õ aka ag…Ēr ug…õ, <Umum ibee umbi awe ra atorh, isi ń©beemum id…õm-Num.>\f + \fr 9.13 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uho 6.6\xt*\ft .\f* Umum isi ń©bamum iyisa abika akaif…õrhk…Ē ug…õ umb…Ē arhika, umum ń©ba iyisa abirab…õ aka ahw…õng ug…õ umb…Ē awu abi arhim.>>
\s1 Arhusa arherhe ikpem ighabin
\r (Umar 2.18-22; Irh 5.33-39)
\p 
\v 14 M…Ēc…õ angw…õŐÉ imesa Uyohana aba arhusa unga, ag…õ, <<Um…õn nggu abi Ufarisi ikpemm…õn ighabin, b…Ēr awu use utsu angw…õŐÉ imesango asi ikpemmb…Ē?>>
\p 
\v 15 M…Ēc…õ Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu use itsu aw…õrhu uner uts…õrh uwuku ufa awe ru idam…õn nu uner ha ana awe nggu umb…Ē? Ivanga niy…Ē ibar…Ē awuri iny√£nguwe uner uts…õrh uwuku ufa ha na ab…Ēre umb…Ē. Ivang h√£ niy…Ē umb…Ē aka ikpem ighabin.
\p 
\v 16 <<Unera asi √≠kŇ© atorho aka afa as…Ēr abipa atorho aka agbe. Ubinkutsu, aka afa ha awuri ishń©rh√£ avaate aka agbe ha. Ivivaar ha iwuri inangge iyi inggbaashia.
\v 17 Ik…õi unera asi √≠tsuka am…õŐÉ inebi aka afa ra amb√£ń© aka agbe. Umb…Ē aba akorhumb…Ē, amb√£ń© h√£ awuri iyar. Am…õŐÉ inebi ha awuri igba, amb√£ń© h√£ awuri iwe ib…õm. ń®'ń©, aka isaka atsu am…õŐÉ inebi aka afa ra amb√£ń© aka afa, nu ake asi √≠yarke ra am…õŐÉ inebi adzek agbake.>>
\s1 Ukom unakuts…õrh nu ukuts…õrh // uwuku ughong
\r (Umar 5.21-43; Irh 8.40-56)
\p 
\v 18 Uyesu anu is…Ēme umb…Ē ak…õr…õ ha, unggbaashi uw…Ē…Ē ru ub√£ if…õn-Nummb…Ē aba atararhu ra anangnga na ag…õ, <<Unapmum anai ikpe. B…Ēr uba utsorhu ubokngo nu unga awuri ib…õka.>>
\v 19 Uyesu asok azń©√£ nggu unga, nu angw…õŐÉ imesanga ad…Ēsa unga.
\p 
\v 20 M…Ēc…õ uts…õrh uw…Ē…Ē aka atsń©√£ im…õka us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn nggu irh√£rh√£ um…õŐÉ…õŐÉ aba ra andzing aba abangu if…õn atorho Uyesu.
\v 21 Unga ag…Ēr ra am…õnnga ag…õ, <<Umum ń©ba ń©bangumum if…õn atorhanga umum iwuri ikerhumum.>>
\p 
\v 22 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka adzipa any√£ unga. Unga ag…õ, <<Niba ugŇ©o ighong unapmum. Imangmangngo ngge ikerhuwa ungo.>> Kanying uts…õrh ha akerhunga.
\p 
\v 23 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka aba atsń© ri iya unggbaashi ha, any√£ abika abar aserhwa nu ikik…Ēng anera iki igwarha arherhe.
\v 24 Unga ag…õ, <<√Äka asombi. Una h√£ anasi ikpea b…Ēr awe ru urh…Ē.>> B…Ēr umb…Ē anyń©rh√£ unga.
\v 25 Anera aka adzek amaa, unga atsń© adzur ubok una h√£, una h√£ asok ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ.
\v 26 Isarhe arherhe ha it…õŐÉrh√£ imaangge abń© h√£.
\s1 Uyesu akerhuwe uner ibvuta // nu igbau
\p 
\v 27 Uyesu aka az…õŐÉrh√£ aneke anang h√£, abi ibvuta avaa ad…Ēsa na atsarhi irhakmb…Ē ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<Ucorhuwa um…õn Ungw…õŐÉ Udauda!>>
\p 
\v 28 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka atsń© ri iya, abi ibvuta ha aba ru unga, unga arhusa umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi awembi ri imangmang ug…õ umum id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ikorhuwamum ak…õr…õ?>>
\p Umb…Ē ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<ń®ń©, Uteijee.>>
\p 
\v 29 Unga abanga asumb…Ē na ag…õ, <<Ri imangmangmbi neke ngge ikorhe ru umbi.>>
\v 30 Asumb…Ē ayanguke. Uyesu agbiite atomb…Ē akarh√£rh√£ ag…õ, <<Niba ad…õyikumbi unera ak…õr…õ ha.>>
\v 31 B…Ēr umb…Ē adzek at…õŐÉrh√£ arherhe ha amaa kishoo abń© h√£.
\p 
\v 32 Umb…Ē aka adzek ra awiya, umb…Ē akŇ© uner uw…Ē…Ē aka awe ru ipfu iyiki ibewe iki ik…õnngge unga arherhe aba ru Uyesu.
\v 33 Ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka awayiwe ipfu iyiki ibewe ha idze, uner igbau ha atirhunga arherhe. Ikik…Ēng anera idzedzeu ni ig…Ēr ig…õ, <<Anasi iny√£mb…Ē ikpŇ© if…õrh…õ rimi ru Uisrairha.>>
\p 
\v 34 B…Ēr abi Ufarisi ag…õ, <<Nggu ijee uy…õrhe √≠pfu iyiki ibewe unga iki ikŇ© atsusuwe √≠pfu iyiki ibewe.>>
\s1 Abi itsera awu ukunjiir
\p 
\v 35 Uyesu ad…Ēsi iteu iyiki ig…Ēng nu iyiki ici kishoo, amesuwe ra ab√£ if…õn-Nummb…Ē. Adzowe Isarhe Iyiki Ize iyi Iy…õrhe af√£, na akerhuwe anera ru kishoo ikpŇ© irh√£rh√£ nu ighighong.
\v 36 Ivangy…õ unga aka any√£ anera aka ak…Ēng arh…õrh…õ, unga agŇ© atorh umb…Ē, ubinkutsu, umb…Ē awe ru uver akarh√£rh√£ na ashimb…Ē ru uner uwuku uyike. Umb…Ē awe ru nyaki √≠d…Ēiy…õ iki ishingge ru uner idz…õu.
\v 37 M…Ēc…õ unga ag…Ēr angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…õ, <<Igb…õra abin iwe irh…õirh…õ, b…Ēr abi itsera awe ukunjiir.
\v 38 √Äka ash…ĒŐÉrhŇ© Uteijee uwu igb…õra abin, unga adene abi itser ri icang igb…õra abinnga.>>
\c 10
\s1 Uyesu ayisa angw…õŐÉ imesanga
\r (Umar 3.13-19; Irh 6.12-16)
\p 
\v 1 Unga aka ayisa angw…õŐÉ imesa us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn aba ru unga, unga adzowe umb…Ē ijee iyiki itsŇ©we √≠pfu iyiki ibewe na akerhuwe ub…õn ikpŇ© irh√£rh√£ nu ighighong.
\p 
\v 2 Atsok abi itser Uyesu ha ak…õ us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn h√£, uwu inbgaashia, Usiman uwu umb…Ē iki iyisa Ubitru, nu Uandarawu ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē, Uyaku ungw…õŐÉ Uzabadi nu Uyohana ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē,
\v 3 Ufirhibu, Ubatorhomi, Utoma nu Umatiyu uner uwuku uy…õisu ikirbi abń©, Uyaku ungw…õŐÉ Uharhfa, Utaddiyu,
\v 4 Usiman uner Ukan'ana nu Uyahuda Uiskariyoti, uwuku ugha adaknga.
\s1 Uyesu adene angw…õŐÉ imesanga
\r (Umar 6.7-13; Irh 9.1-6)
\p 
\v 5 Uyesu adene us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn h√£ ag…õ, <<Niba azń©mbi ra atsen abi Uyahuda use atsń© ru ub…õn uteu Usamariya.
\v 6 √Äka azń© ri √≠d…Ēi iyiki igwir iyi Uisrairha.
\v 7 Ri izizń©mbi, √†ka adzowe isarhe iy…õr…õ ag…õ, <Iy…õrhe af√£ iki iyongge.>
\v 8 √Äka akerhuwe abi irh√£rh√£, √†ka azituwe abika akpe, √†ka asare abi ingbim, √†ka atsusuwe √≠pfu iyiki ibewe. Umbi ay…õi ijee ha izŇ©w√£, √†ka at…ĒŐÉ itser nggu ngge izŇ©w√£.
\v 9 Niba akp…Ēmmbi uzinarhi use uazurhfa use ubinkpi uku uwu ru nyaku uhw…õk ri ibvukmbi.
\v 10 Niba nyangumbi ukpoka ru uz…õŐÉrh√£ h√£, use atorho avaa, use abadak avaa use igbong, ubinkutsu, uner itser am…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ikpo ubingha.
\p 
\v 11 <<Ub…õn uteu ukug…Ēng use uku uci umbi aka itsń©, √†ka abee uner uwuku urhurhika um…Ē. √Äka asei ri iyanga uts…õku isisokmbi.
\v 12 Ivangy…õ umbi aka itsń© ri iya ha, √†ka aghwe umb…Ē.
\v 13 Iya ha iba ibemuke umbi, neke idid…Ē…Ērambi iwe um…Ē, b…Ēr ike iba isi ibemuke, idid…Ē…Ērambi ibvui iba ru umbi.
\v 14 Unera aba asi iy…õisa umbi use akpea ato ra arherhambi, √†ka awashuwe uzurhu uwu adakmbi ivangy…õ umbi aka idze ri iya ha use uteu ha.
\v 15 Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, uver uteu ha use iya ha uwuri unangkp…Ē ukpu aner Us…Ēd…Ēm nu Ugomora ru unum ukpuku uvarha arherhe.
\s1 Ayetnum ak…Ē abar…Ē
\r (Umar 13.9-13; Irh 12.11-12; 21.12-19)
\p 
\v 16 <<Umum idena umbi adzek ru nyaka √≠d…Ēi ra ateu √≠jui ngbako. Nggee √†ka awe ru itsoi ru nyaki √≠bvui na ashimbi ri iki ibewe ru nyaka anurh…õu.
\p 
\v 17 <<√Äka akp…Ēm am…õnmbi nggu anera, umb…Ē awuri iden umbi ra ateu akakŇ© na akw…õr umbi ra ab√£ if…õn-Nummb…Ē.
\v 18 Ri itsimbi aka ad…Ēsa umum, umb…Ē awuri ikŇ©na umbi azń© ra asu agomna nu ay…õrhe ru nyaka abi idekamum ru umb…Ē nu atsen abi Uyahuda.
\v 19 B…Ēr ivangy…õ umb…Ē aka idzur umbi, niba agŇ©mbi ighong ubinkpi umbi aka irherhe use umbi irherhe uguse. Ri ivang h√£ awuri idzaamb…Ē ubinkpi umbi aka irherhe.
\v 20 Asi √≠wea umbi irherhe, b…Ēr Ipfu Ut…õmbi ngge irherhe ra angwń©mbi.
\p 
\v 21 <<Ungw…õŐÉyi awuri idzowe ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē umb…Ē af…õre, utei ik…õi awuri idzowe ungw…õŐÉnga. Aw…õkaci ik…õi awuri iwu ri igamtsak nggu ateimb…Ē uts…õku umb…Ē aka itsu umb…Ē af…õre umb…Ē.
\v 22 Anera kishoo awuri ikp…õŐÉna umbi ri itsokmum. B…Ēr kishoo uwuku ubima uts…õku imimasha awuri ikpoa ifif…Ērh.
\v 23 Umb…Ē aba adzaamb…Ē umbi uver ra anang ak…Ē…Ē, √†ka atń© azń© anang ak…Ē…Ē. Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner awuri ibanga nu umbi anasi imaambi itsń©rhń© iteu Uisrairha kishoo.
\p 
\v 24 <<Ungw…õŐÉ imesa asi inanga umarhemnga, use ug√£rh√£ ananga uteiyanga.
\v 25 Ungw…õŐÉ imesa awe ra angg…Ēm unga aka awe ru nyaku umarhemnga nu ug√£rh√£ ru nyaku uteiyanga. Umb…Ē aba ayisa umum iki iwe uteiyambi ug…õ Uba'arhzaburh uy…õrhe √≠pfu iyiki ibewe, awuri iyisa umbi nggu itsok ha anangmb…Ē umum!
\s1 Unerwi aka am…õŐÉ umb…Ē agŇ© iwei unga
\r (Irh 12.8-9)
\p 
\v 26 <<Nggee niba agŇ©mbi iwei umb…Ē. Ubin ushikp…Ē umb…Ē aka af…Ēm, ukp…Ē uku usi √≠dzekp…Ē, use ri iw…Ēk umb…Ē aka asi √≠hw…õngmb…Ē.
\v 27 Abink…õ umum iki is…Ēma umbi ru uzń©, √†ka as…Ēme ake ri irhirhang. Abink…õ aka akh…õwa ra atombi, √†ka adŇ©w√£ ake ra atsi uvi.
\v 28 Niba agŇ©mbi iwei abika af…õre iyor b…Ēr asi √≠d…õŐÉ…õŐÉ af…õrmb…Ē ipfu. Nu ngge iki iwe rimi, aka agŇ© iwei uwuruwi aka id…õŐÉ…õŐÉ af…õre iyor nu ipfu kishoo ri idzŇ© urha.
\v 29 Asi iwea ahwirhg…Ēm avaa umb…Ē aki igoshe ukobo unying? Nggee unying usi √≠gbamgb…Ē ra abń© Ut…õmbi aka asi √≠hw…õnga umgb…Ē.
\v 30 Nu uko √≠gwar itsimbi umb…Ē aka avuvarha ngge.
\v 31 Nggee niba agŇ©mbi iwei, umbi anangmbi ahwirhg…Ēm ugarh idiki irh…õirh…õ.
\p 
\v 32 <<Ub…õn unera aka ad…õyiwe itsinga ug…õ unga awu uwu umum ra asu anera, umum iwuri id…õyikŇ© unga awu uwu umum ra asu Ut…õmum ra af√£.
\v 33 B…Ēr ub…õn unera aka ats…õyinga ihw…õng umum ra asu anera, umum iwuri itsits…õyimum ihw…õng unga ra asu Ut…õmum ra af√£.
\s1 Asi iwea idid…Ē…Ēr b…Ēr awu ifuw
\r (Irh 12.51-53; 14.26-27)
\p 
\v 34 <<Niba akaimbi if…õrhk…Ē ug…õ umum ń©ba itsu idid…Ē…Ēr ru upfung. Umum isi ń©bamum itsu idid…Ē…Ēr, b…Ēr ikŇ© ifuw.
\v 35 Ubinkutsu, umum ń©ba itsu ifuw ru,
\q1 << <ungw…õŐÉ nu ut…õnga,
\q2 unai nu uyanga,
\q1 uts…õn ungw…õŐÉ nu ukokanga.
\q2 
\v 36 Anggamtsak unera awuri iwe abi iyanga.>\f + \fr 10.36 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Umik 7.6\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 37 <<Uwuruwi aka abemu uyanga use ut…õnga ananga umum asi im…õŐÉ…õŐÉ iwe uwu umum. Uwuruwi aka abemu ungw…õŐÉnga use unapunga ananga umum, asi im…õŐÉ…õŐÉ iwe uwu umum.
\v 38 Ub…õn unera aka asi ishupu ig√£rh√£mau ucuciianga ad…Ēsunga umum, asi im…õŐÉ…õŐÉ iwe uwu umum.
\v 39 Uwuruwi aka akpo urh…õnga, unga awuri igwirhe umgb…Ē, nu uwuruwi aka agwirhuwe urh…õnga ri itsimum, awuri ikpoa umgb…Ē.
\s1 Itser itosa
\r (Umar 9.41)
\p 
\v 40 <<Uwuruwi aka ay…õi umbi, ay…õi umum. Uwuruwi aka ay…õi umum ay…õi uwuku udena umum.
\v 41 Uwuruwi aka ay…õi uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num ri itsernga, awuri iy…õisa itosa uner uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num. Nu ub…õn uwuku uy…õi uner uwuku urhika ri irhirhikanga awuri iy…õisa itosa iyi uner uwuku urhika.
\v 42 Nu uwuruwi aka adzowe uko ukp…õwa am…õŐÉ aka agh…õnga ru ub…õn unera ra ab…õr…õ aka awe angw…õŐÉ imesamum, umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, awuri ikpoa itosanga.>>
\c 11
\s1 Uyesu nu Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima
\r (Irh 7.18-35)
\p 
\v 1 Uyesu aka amaa imesuwe angw…õŐÉ imesanga us…ĒkdŇ©m…õn h√£, unga adzek um…Ē azń© amesuwe na adzowe isarhe ra abń© Ugarhirhi.
\p 
\v 2 Ivangy…õ Uyohana ru ugborzń© aka agŇ© abink…õ Ukiristo aka akorhe, unga adene angw…õŐÉ imesanga
\v 3 azń© arhusa unga ag…õ, <<Awu ungo uwu uwuku ububa ha, use um…õn itsu asum…õn ru uw…Ē…Ē?>>
\p 
\v 4 Uyesu adzipa ag…õ, <<√Äka abvui azń© ad…õyiwe Uyohana ubinkpi umbi aka agŇ© na any√£.
\v 5 Abi ibvuta any√£mb…Ē, akatarhu az…õŐÉrhŇ©mb…Ē uz…õŐÉrh√£, abi ingbim akerhumb…Ē, abi igbau agŇ©mb…Ē, ikom isongge nggu urh…õ, adzowukumb…Ē Isarhe Iyiki Ize ra atsŇ©w√£.
\v 6 Idorh iwu iyi uwu ha aka asi ikp…õŐÉ…õŐÉ umum ri itsi abink…õ umum iki ikorhe.>>
\p 
\v 7 Ivangy…õ aw…õ imesu Uyohana aka azń©mb…Ē, Uyesu atirha arherhe nggu ikik…Ēnga ri itsi Uyohana ag…õ, <<Umbi azń© iz…õrhu use ra arhum? Ubń©ń© uku uder ugba iki if…õu?
\v 8 Iba ishingge rimi, ude umbi adzek azń© iz…õrhu use? Utsa uw…Ē…Ē aka atsim atorho aka aze? ń®'ń©, abika atsim atorho aka aze asei ra adzepurhe iy…õrhe.
\v 9 Ude umbi adzek azń© iz…õrhu use? Uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num? ń®ń©, umum id…õyiwa umbi, ananga uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num.
\v 10 Unga h√£ uwi umb…Ē aka ats…õng ra Arherhu-Num ri itsinga ag…õ,
\q1 << <Umum iwuri idene ungw…õŐÉ itsermum agbaashia ru ungo.
\q2 Unga awuri igbishuwa atsń©ndń©ngo.>\f + \fr 11.10 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Umrh 3.1\xt*\ft .\f*
\m 
\v 11 Umum ind…õyiwa umbi idzidz…õrhe, ra abirab…õ akats…õrh aka amar asi itsń©mb…Ē Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima. B…Ēr uwuruwi aka awu uku ucia ri Iy…õrhe af√£, ananga unga.
\v 12 Udzur ri ivang Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima uba utsń© irher…õ, Iy…õrhe af√£ iwe ru uver, abika adzowe uver ha umb…Ē abee ivur ngge ri iker.
\v 13 Ubinkutsu kishoo its…õng abika as…Ēm Arherhu-Num nu √ćkpem Umusa irherhungge arherhe ak…õr…õ uts…õku ivang Uyohana.
\v 14 Umbi aba ibemumbi ubinkpi umum iki irherhe, Uyohana unga awu Uirhiya ha umb…Ē aka arherhe ug…õ unga awuri ibanga.
\v 15 Neke uner uwuku uwu ra ato aka agŇ©, unga agŇ©.
\p 
\v 16 <<Umum ikpangu udan ukpir…õ nggu use? Awu ru nyaka aw…õkaci iki isei ra anang iz…õ…õ na ayisa ab…Ē…Ē ag…õ,
\q1 
\v 17 << <Um…õn ibara umbi aserhuwa,
\q2 umbi akp…õŐÉmbi izer.
\q1 Um…õn itsŇ© ubom akpe,
\q2 umbi akp…õŐÉmbi iciu akpe.>
\m 
\v 18 Uyohana aka aba, asi itsuka am…õnnga ri ighigha nu ihwihwa, umb…Ē ag…õ, <Unga awe ru ipfu iyiki ibewe.>
\v 19 Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner aka aba agha na ahwa, umb…Ē ag…õ, <√Äka any√£ uner uwuku ubvun igha abin nu ihwihwa akarh√£rh√£, uw…õrh…õ abika ay…õi ikirbi abń© nu abi arhim!> B…Ēr awu itser unera iwuri id…õyiwe ug…õ unga awea ri itsoi.>>
\s1 Atorh iteuy…õ iki inasi idzipungge
\r (Irh 10.13-15)
\p 
\v 20 M…Ēc…õ Uyesu aka atirhi its…õyi iteuy…õ unga aka akorhe irh…õ abin idzeu ri ngge, ubinkutsu, anera asi idzipumb…Ē.
\v 21 <<Atorhngo, Ukorazin! Atorhngo Ubetsaida! Ag…õ itser idzeu ha umb…Ē aka at…ĒŐÉ ru umbi, umb…Ē at…ĒŐÉmb…Ē ngge ru Utaya nu Usidon, umb…Ē awuri idzipumb…Ē iki ifitem, umb…Ē awuri itsim ashaka atorho, na asei ra at…Ē…Ē.
\v 22 B…Ēr umum id…õyiwa umbi, ru unum ukpuku uvarha arherhe, uvermbi uwuri inangkp…Ē ukpu Utaya nu Usidon.
\v 23 Ungo igango, Ukafanahum, ungo ukaif…õrhk…Ē ug…õ awuri ibera ungo afŇ© af√£? ń®'ń©, awuri ikŇ©na ungo acipa ra anang isei abika akpukpe. Itser idzeuy…õ umb…Ē aka at…ĒŐÉ ru ungo umb…Ē aba at…ĒŐÉ ngge ru Us…Ēd…Ēm, ukp…Ē uba uwe um…Ē uts…õku irher…õ.
\v 24 B…Ēr umum id…õyiwa umbi ru unum ukpuku uvarha arherhe, uvermbi uwuri inangkp…Ē ukpu Us…Ēd…Ēm.>>
\s1 √Äka aba ru umum na akpo iwiwosha
\r (10.21-22)
\p 
\v 25 Ri ivang h√£ Uyesu awu ra angg…Ēm ri Ipfu Isarsatangge, ag…Ēr ag…õ, <<Umum ikpoi ungo Ut…õ, Uteijee uwu af√£ nggu abń©, ungo uku uw…Ēk…Ē if…õrh…õ iy…õr…õ ru abi itsoi nu abi idzursu, nu us…Ēme ake ra aw…õkaci.
\v 26 A Ut…õ, ak…õr…õ ha awu ubinkpi ungo uku ugŇ©ib…õn ikorha ukp…Ē.
\p 
\v 27 <<Ut…õmum adzaa abina kishoo ru umum. Unera asi ihw…õnga am…õn Ungw…õŐÉ…õŐÉ, Ut…õ ikiyikanga ahw…õng. Unera asi ihw…õngnga am…õn Utei, Ungw…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ukpekŇ© nu uwuruwi Ungw…õŐÉ h√£ aka is…Ēme unga.
\p 
\v 28 <<√Äka aba ru umum, kishoo umbi abika agŇ© azhe na agŇ© imor, umum iwuri idzaamum umbi iwiwosha.
\v 29 √Äka adzowe atsimbi na amesa ru umum, ubinkutsu, umum iwu uner inna nu idid…Ē…Ēr ra am…õnmum, nu umbi awuri ikpombi iwiwosha ra am…õnmbi.
\v 30 Ubinkutsu, idzowe itsimbi ru umum asi iwea ubin uku ughong, abinmum asi imorke.>>
\c 12
\s1 Uteijee uwu unum ukpuku uwosha
\r (Umar 2.23-28; Irh 6.1-5)
\p 
\v 1 Ri ivang h√£ Uyesu az…õŐÉrh√£ at…Ēng ri √≠cang uarhkama ru unum ukpuku uwosha. Angw…õŐÉ imesanga agŇ© imerh umb…Ē atirhi igbiu isha arhkama h√£ at√£i.
\v 2 Ivang abi Ufarisi aka any√£ rimi, umb…Ē ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<Uny√£! Angw…õŐÉ imesango aka azharhuwe Ikpem unum ukpuku uwosha.>>
\p 
\v 3 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Umbi anasi ivarhumbi ubinkpi Udauda aka akorhe ri ivangy…õ unga nggu aw…õrhu uz…õŐÉrh√£nga aka agŇ© imerh?
\v 4 Unga aka atsń© ru Iya-Num anyangu usarkasar uborodi at√£i nggu aw…õrhu uz…õŐÉrh√£nga, ukpurukpi ri Ikpem awu abika adzowe id…õm-Num ukpekŇ© iki it√£i.
\v 5 Use umbi anasi ivarhumbi ri √ćkpem Umusa ug…õ abika adzowe id…õm-Num ri itser unum ukpuku uwosha ri Iya-Num aka adakuwe unum ukpuku uwosha na ishimb…Ē ru uvau?
\v 6 Umum id…õyiwa umbi uwuruwi aka ananga Iya-Num awu nggimi.
\v 7 Umbi aba ahw…õngmbi agben its…õng Arherhu-Num h√£ iki ig…Ēr ig…õ, <Umum ibee umbi awe ra atorh, isi ń©beemum id…õm-Num,>\f + \fr 12.7 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uho 6.6\xt*\ft .\f* Umbi aba asi itsumbi uvau ra abika asheru uvau.
\v 8 Ubinkutsu Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner awu Uteijee unum ukpuku uwosha.>>
\s1 Uner ushayi ubok
\r (Umar 3.1-6; Irh 6.6-11)
\p 
\v 9 Adzeka anang h√£ unga atsń©√£ ru ub√£ if…õn-Nummb…Ē.
\v 10 Uner uw…Ē…Ē uboka uku ushayi awu um…Ē. Umb…Ē abee udń©kpi umb…Ē aka ikpo Uyesu nggu uvau, umb…Ē arhusa unga ag…õ, <<Ri Ikpem im…õŐÉngge umb…Ē akerhuwe ru unum ukpuku uwosha?>>
\p 
\v 11 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Unera ru umbi aba awuri id…Ēi ngge igba ru ughwee ru unum ukpuku uwosha, uner id…Ēi ha asi √≠dzur akp…Ēm ngge atsŇ©wŇ©ka?
\v 12 Unera ananga id…Ēi akarh√£rh√£! Nggee asi iwea izharhuwe Ikpem ri ikorhi iyiki ize ru unum ukpuku uwosha.>>
\p 
\v 13 M…Ēc…õ unga ag…Ēr utsak ha ag…õ, <<Unamu ubokngo udzek.>> Nggee unga anamu uboknga udzek, ukp…Ē ukerhe uwe ru nyaku ukpu uvaa.
\v 14 B…Ēr abi Ufarisi adzek ak…õki itsŇ©w√£ umb…Ē aka if…õre Uyesu.
\s1 Itsuif…õr is…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uishaya
\p 
\v 15 Ivang Uyesu aka ahw…õng rimi, unga ab…Ēruka anang h√£. Arh…õrh…õ aka ad…Ēsa unga, unga akerhuwe irh√£rh√£mb…Ē.
\v 16 Unga agbiite atomb…Ē ug…õ niba ad…õyikumb…Ē iwiwenga ru unera.
\v 17 Ak…õr…õ ake atsuaf…õr ubinkpi uku urherhe ra angwń© uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uishaya ag…õ,
\q1 
\v 18 <<Uny√£ ug√£rh√£mum uwi umum iki is…õng,
\q2 uwu umum iki ń©bema,
\q1 ru unga umum iki igŇ©ib…õn.
