\p 
\v 38 M…Ēc…õ abi Ufarisi ab…Ē…Ē nu abika amesuwe Ikpem ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<A umarhem, um…õn ibee iny√£ utsar idzeu ru ungo.>>
