\v 27 <<Ag√£rhŇ© uner icang h√£ aba ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <A uteiya, ungo usi idos…Ē ikpŇ© iyiki ize ri icangngo? Ubń©ń© udzek…õ ukp…Ē?>
