\v 28 <<Unga ag…õ, <Awu unggamtsakmum unga akorha aki ha.>
\p <<Ag√£rh√£ ha ag…õ, <Ungo ubeengo um…õn izń© iz…Ēnge ubń©√£ h√£?>
\p 
\v 29 <<Unga ag…õ, <ń®'ń©, ubinkutsu, umbi aba awuri iz…Ēngmbi ubń©ń© ri itsem h√£, umbi ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ abvurhkumbi itsema nggu ubń©√£ h√£.
\v 30 √Äka aneke ake aseng urh…Ēnga uts…õku ivang iyiki ititeng. Ri ivang h√£ umum iwuri ń©d…õyikŇ© abi aka ateng h√£, umb…Ē agbaashia ateng ubń©√£ h√£ apfuma, aboyi ats√£ ats√£, umb…Ē akpń©ń©we, b…Ēr akarhi itsema aba atsuku ungbanmum.> >>
\s1 Unyaka arherhe ishaa ikpŇ© iyiki ici
