\v 44 <<Iy…õrhe af√£ iwu ru nyaka abin ugarh aka aw…Ēk ri icang. Ivangy…õ unera aka akpo ake, unga aw…Ēke ake ik…õi, ag…Ēm na azń© agoshe kishoo abinnga na agoi icang h√£.
\s1 Unyaka arherhe utarh ukpuku // uwe ru ugarh
