\v 45 <<Iy…õrhe af√£ iwu ru nyaku uner igoi uwuku ubee atarhk…õ aka awu ru ugarh.
\v 46 Ivangy…õ unga aka akpo utarh ugarh ha akarh√£rh√£, unga azń© agoshuka kishoo abink…õ unga aka awe ra ake na agoi utarh ugarh ha.
\s1 Unyaka arherhe itang igber
