\v 47 <<Iy…õrhe af√£ iwe ru nyaki itang igber iyiki idzui ab…õrh. Umb…Ē iki itang ru ukau ukug…Ēng ngge idzui kishoo ikpŇ© ab…õrh.
\v 48 Ivangy…õ ngge iki it…Ēk, abi ud…õm agbiir azń© ru ubang ukau ukug…Ēng h√£. M…Ēc…õ umb…Ē asei na at…õng ab…õrh aka azea atsuku uzing na atare akika abewe.
\v 49 Iwuri iwe rimi ri imimashu upfung. √ćpfu itser-Num iwuri iba igashuwe abika abewe nggu abika arhurhika.
\v 50 Umb…Ē awuri itare abika abewunga ri ikon urha, ra anangk…õ umb…Ē aka iciu akpe na at√£i anyń©.>>
\p 
\v 51 Uyesu arhusa ag…õ, <<Umbi ahw…õngmbi ak…õr…õ ha kishoo?>>
\p Umb…Ē ag…õ, <<ń®ń©.>>
\p 
\v 52 Unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Nggee ub…õn uwuku umesuwe Ikpem umb…Ē aka ad…õyiwe unga Iy…õrhe af√£, awe ru nyaku utei iya aka akŇ© abin adzeka ru angbannga aka afa nu aka agbe.>>
\s1 Akp…õŐÉmb…Ē Uyesu ru Unazarat
\r (Umar 6.1-6; Irh 4.16-30)
\p 
\v 53 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka amaa unyaka arherhe ak…õr…õ, unga ab…Ēruka anang h√£.
\v 54 Ivangy…õ unga aka aba utepunga, unga atirhi imesuwe anera ru ub√£ if…õn-Nummb…Ē. Umb…Ē adzeidzeu na arhusa ag…õ, <<Utsak uwur…õ akpo itsoi iy…õr…õ rin…õ…õ rimi nu ijee iyiki ikorha abin idzeu?
\v 55 Asi iwea uw…õr…õ ha awu ungw…õŐÉ ukapinta ha? Asi iwea uyanga umb…Ē iki iyisa Umaryamu? Asi iwea angw…õŐÉmb…Ē rab…õ, umb…Ē Uyaku nu Uyusuf nu Usiman nu Uyahuda?
\v 56 Asi iwea kishoo anapumb…Ē rab…õ nggu um…õn? Awu rin…õ…õ unga aka akpo kishoo abin ak…õr…õ ha?>>
\v 57 M…Ēc…õ umb…Ē agŇ© av…Ēm nggu unga.
\p B…Ēr Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu ru ub…õn unera aka adzowe uner uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num ig…Ēng, b…Ēr asi iwea abi utepunga, nu abi iyanga.>>
\p 
\v 58 Awu ida imangmangmb…Ē itsu unga asi ikorhunga abin idzeu arh…õrh…õ ngg…Ē…Ē ha.
\c 14
\s1 Akpe Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima
