\p 
\v 1 Ri ivang h√£ Uy…õrhe Uhiridu aka agŇ© arherhe ri itsi Uyesu.
\v 2 Unga ag…Ēr abika at…ĒŐÉwe unga itser ag…õ, <<Awu Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima unga asok ra akpe! Ngge itsu unga awuri ijee iyiki ikorha abin idzeu ak…õr…õ.>>
\p 
\v 3 Ubinkutsu Uhiridu aka adzur Uyohana agbang ru ugborzń© ri itsi Uhirudiya uts…õrha ungw…õŐÉmb…Ē Ufirhibu.
