\c 15
\s1 Isisar nu ida isisar
\r (Umar 7.1-13)
\p 
\v 1 M…Ēc…õ abi Ufarisi ab…Ē…Ē nu abika amesuwe Ikpem adzeku Urusharhima aba ru Uyesu arhusa ag…õ,
\v 2 <<Awu use utsu angw…õŐÉ imesango azharhuwe agbeyi atokam…õn? Asi isorhmb…Ē abokmb…Ē na ad…Ērha agha ubingha.>>
\p 
\v 3 B…Ēr Uyesu ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Awu use utsu agbeyambi atsu umbi azharhuwe Ikpem Unum?
\v 4 Ubinkutsu Unum ag…õ, <Udzowe imor ru ut…õngo nu uyango,>\f + \fr 15.4 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Idzi 20.12; Iva 5.16\xt*\ft .\f* nu <Ub…õn unera aka arhenu ut…õnga use uyanga awu ufang umb…Ē af…õre unga.>\f + \fr 15.4 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Idzi 21.17; Urha 20.9\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 5 B…Ēr umbi amesuwe ug…õ ub…õn unera aba awea ru ubinkpi unga aka iyike ut…õnga use uyanga, na ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <Ubin h√£ uwu izŇ©w√£ iyi Unum.>
\v 6 Rimi h√£ umbi ag…õ asi iwea ufang unga idzowe imor ut…õnga nggu ukp…Ē. Agbeyambi atsu umbi anyanga Arherhu-Num awe ib…õm.
\v 7 Umbi abi ukpukpeta! Irhikungge uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uishaya aka as…Ēm arherhe ri itsimbi ag…õ,
\q1 
\v 8 << <Aner ab…õr…õ adzaa umum ig…Ēng nggu angwń©mb…Ē ukpekŇ©,
\q2 b…Ēr am…õnmb…Ē aderke nggu umum.
\q1 
\v 9 Umb…Ē adzaa umum ig…Ēng ib…õm,
\q2 anu imesuwe ikpem anera ug…õ…õ Unum adzowe umb…Ē.> \f + \fr 15.9 \ft √Äka any√£ ik…õi: \xt Uish 29.13\xt*\ft .\f*>>
\s1 Abink…õ aka awuri itsu ida isisar
\r (Umar 7.14-23)
\p 
\v 10 Uyesu ayisi ikik…Ēnga iba ru unga ag…Ēr umb…Ē ag…õ, <<√Äka akpeto na ahw…õng.
\v 11 Asi iwea ubinkpi iki itsń© ra angwń© unera itsu unga asi isara, b…Ēr ubinkpi uku idzeka ra angwń©nga, ukp…Ē…Ē utsu unga <asi isara.> >>
\p 
\v 12 M…Ēc…õ angw…õŐÉ imesanga aba ru unga arhusa ag…õ, <<Ungo uhw…õngngo abi Ufarisi agŇ© av…Ēm umb…Ē aka agŇ© arherha ak…õr…õ?>>
\p 
\v 13 Unga ag…õ, <<Ub…õn ubinkpi Ut…õmum ra af√£ aka asi idosa, awuri ibvurhuwe.
\v 14 √Äka aneke umb…Ē, umb…Ē awu abi ibvuta abika adarh abi ibvuta. Uner ibvuta aba adarha uner ibvuta, umb…Ē ikivarhamb…Ē awuri igba ru ughwee.>>
