\p 
\v 27 Unga ag…õ, <<ń®ń©, Uteijee, b…Ēr √≠jui iki isaki ighangge awushu ubingha aki idzeku utebur iyi uteiya agbei nu abń©.>>
\p 
\v 28 M…Ēc…õ Uyesu ag…Ēr unga ag…õ, <<A ats…õrh ha, imangmango iwe akarh√£rh√£! Ibibeeango ikpongge.>> Kanying unapunga akerhunga.
\s1 Uyesu akerhuwe anera arh…õrh…õ
\p 
\v 29 Uyesu ab…Ēre um…Ē na ad…Ēsu udiku ubang Ukau Ugarhirhi. M…Ēc…õ unga afŇ© igŇ© aseisa.
\v 30 Nggaa ikik…Ēng iba ru unga, akŇ© akatarhu, nu abi ibvuta, nu abika akaikai, nu abika af…Ēr arherhe adamb…Ē, nu ab…Ē…Ē arh…õrh…õ, aden umb…Ē ra adaknga, nu unga akerhuwe umb…Ē.
\v 31 Anera adzeidzeu umb…Ē aka any√£ agbau arherha arherhe, abika akaikai ayormb…Ē akerhuke, akatarhu az…õŐÉrhŇ©mb…Ē uz…õŐÉrh√£, abi ibvuta any√£mb…Ē. Nu umb…Ē kishoo akpoi Unum uwu Uisrairha.
\s1 Uyesu afuka anera // anakag…Ēnga anaa
