\v 36 M…Ēc…õ unga anyangu √≠po uborodi ha ut…Ē…Ēva nu ab…õrh ha, unga aka atar uw…õ…õ ru Unum. M…Ēc…õ na ats…Ēka ukp…Ē adzowe angw…õŐÉ imesanga, umb…Ē agashuwe ikik…Ēng anera.
\v 37 Kishoo agha ashur. Angw…õŐÉ imesanga arh…ĒŐÉyń© awushunga ra abń© ake at…Ēk azń©nga ut…Ē…Ēva.
\v 38 Abirab…õ aka agha akatsak awu anakag…Ēnga anaa, asi ivarhumb…Ē akats…õrh nu aw…õkaci.
\v 39 Uyesu aka asoyiwe ikik…Ēng anera amaa, unga atsń© ukhukh…Ē…Ē am…õŐÉ azń©√£ abń© Umagadan.
\c 16
\s1 Umb…Ē abee utsar
\r (Umar 8.11-13; Irh 12.54-56)
\p 
\v 1 Abi Ufarisi nu abi Usaduki aba aviru Uyesu, arhusa unga ug…õ unga akorhu ubin idzeu ukpu uwu utsar uku udzeka af√£.
\p 
\v 2 Unga ag…õ, <<Urh…õ…õ uba uwekp…Ē, umbi aka isaka ag…Ēr ag…õ, <Ananga awuri izeke ud√£, af√£ awe uku uzh√£√£ń©.>
\v 3 Nu unkpeeka umbi aba any√£ af√£ awe uku uzh√£√£ń© na atsir nggu ufin inai, umbi aka isaka ag…Ēr ag…õ, <Irher…õ inai iwuri idoingge.> Umbi ad…õŐÉ…õŐÉ ahw…õngmbi agben af√£, b…Ēr umbi asi ihw…õngmbi atsark…õ aka id…õyiwe agben abink…õ aka anu ikorhe inum iy…õr…õ.
\v 4 Abika abewe, abika asheru Unum, abi undan ukpir…õ arhusu utsar idzeu! B…Ēr asi √≠d…õyikumb…Ē umb…Ē utsar, akpurha ad…õyiwe utsar ukpu uwuku us…Ēm Arherhu-Num Uyunana.>> Uyesu ab…Ēre umb…Ē na azń©√£.
\s1 Uga abi Ufarisi nu uwu // abi Usaduki
\r (Umar 8.14-21)
