\p 
\v 13 Ivangy…õ Uyesu aka aba ra abń© abi Ukaisariya Ufirhibi, unga arhusa angw…õŐÉ imesanga ag…õ, <<Anera ani ig…Ēr ug…õ Ungw…õŐÉ-Ner awu ungam…Ē?>>
\p 
\v 14 Umb…Ē ag…õ, <<Ab…Ē…Ē ag…Ēr ug…õ Uyohana Uner Ub…Ētisima, ab…Ē…Ē ag…õ Uirhiya, ab…Ē…Ē ag…õ Uirimiya use uw…Ē…Ē ra abika as…Ēm Arherhu-Num.>>
